Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当我走进这家非常豪华的酒店时 ‪我感觉很不自在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}When I walk into this really fancy hotel, I feel out of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我想我来得有点早 ‪所以我决定坐着等会儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I think I'm a bit early. So I just decide to sit down and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我已经到了）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你会很紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}You know, you're nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当电梯门终于打开时）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}When the elevator door finally pings...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我心里想 “天啊”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was like, "Shit."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他看起来和照片上一模一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He looks exactly like his pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他有这种吸引力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He has this magnetism.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这人有些特别的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}There's something about this guy that is special.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们最初讨论的话题之一 ‪就是他的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}One of the first topics we talked about was his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他是LLD钻石公司的总裁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He's the CEO of LLD Diamonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（LLD钻石公司 列维耶夫集团公司）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他从他父亲手中接任了这份工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He got the job from his dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他提到他爸爸是钻石之王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}When he mentioned that his dad was the king of diamonds,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这就意味着他是钻石王子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}so that meant that he was the prince of diamonds,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我意识到 “天啊 ‪这是个什么样的家庭啊”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I realized, like, "My God, what kind of family is this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪很快 他就会变得非常私人化 ‪这就是我喜欢这一切的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Very quickly, he'd become very personal. And that's what I really liked about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他有一个再过几周就满两岁的女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He has a baby daughter that turns two in a couple of weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪她目前在伦敦探望他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}She's there now to visit him in London,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但他和孩子妈妈已经不在一起了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}but he's not together with the mom anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他很少长时间待在一个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He's rarely in one place for a very long period of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他很怀念拥有一个人的感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and he just missed having someone, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当我们的约会快结束时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}When we were nearing the end of the date,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他说 “我真的很想更好地了解你”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}he said, "I really want to get to know you better."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他们要去保加利亚出差\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}They were traveling to Bulgaria for a business trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后他问我想不想和他们一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and then he was asking me if I wanted to join them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们是乘私人飞机出游的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We're traveling by private jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“靠 这是我以前从未做过的新事”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"Shit. Ooh, this is something new that I've never done before."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我觉得如果我拒绝 就太蠢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I felt that I would be stupid if I said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以我内心非常激动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So I was kind of, like, super excited on the inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但表面上我保持冷静 因为我在想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}but on the outside, I kept it very cool, because I was just thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“好吧 你喜欢这个人 ‪你现在就是需要保持冷静”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"Okay, you like this guy, you just need to keep your cool now."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙让他的一个司机送我回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon asked one of his drivers to take me back home,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪以便我打包行李 并拿上护照\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}so I could pack some stuff, get my passport,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后他们会开车送我回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}then they will drive me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪突然间 有辆劳斯莱斯在等我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Suddenly, there's this Rolls-Royce waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪于是我心想 “天啊 这太疯狂了”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So I was kind of like, "My God. This is insane."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这感觉就像在电影里一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It felt like being in a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（阿纳托利·德·格伦沃尔德制作）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪米高梅公司出品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪一个令人兴奋的 ‪奢侈的 浪漫冒险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}an exciting, extravagant, romantic adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪黄色的劳斯莱斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The Yellow Rolls-Royce.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我第一次打包行李时速度很快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I can be quick when I pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我和我的闺蜜们有一个聊天群\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I have a messenger group with my girlfriends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我今天要坐私人飞机了）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（等等）什么）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我的朋友们都吓坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}My friends are freaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（天啊））
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（不是吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（这听起来不安全）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“这人是谁 你是怎么认识他的 ‪你可能会被绑架”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"Who is this guy? How do you know him? You can be abducted."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我当时说 “我都没想过这种事 ‪我就是在约会”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was like, "Oh, I didn't even think about that. I'm on a date, you know."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（及时行乐）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪到了机场 ‪有一整个团队都在等着我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}At the airport, there is the entire team waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪一个很高的人 我猜他就是保镖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}A really tall guy, which I presume is the bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪有几个司机 还有他的小女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}There's a couple of drivers, and you have his little daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我看到了西蒙女儿身边的这个女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I see this woman that's with Simon's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙告诉我那是孩子的妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon tells me that that's the baby's mother
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪她们会和我们一起上飞机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and that they're going to be on the plane with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他的前妻要加入我们的第一次约会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}His ex is joining us on our first date together,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我心里想 “好吧 这一定很有趣”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and I'm kind of like, "Well, this can be interesting."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪早上好 你好吗 很好 早上好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Morning. How are you? Ah, good. Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你在飞机上拍视频了吗 ‪能给我看看吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Did you take videos on the plane? Show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪拍了 那感觉就像是最差劲的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Yes. It's like the worst person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我的一个朋友就是这么说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}That's what one of my friends would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.76,0:11:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“你能不能别表现得那么尴尬吗” ‪但我当时真的非常兴奋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"Can you stop being so awkward?" But I was very excited about it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那里有香槟和鱼子酱 ‪我之前从未吃过鱼子酱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It was champagne with caviar. I've never eaten caviar before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后还有寿司 ‪那里就像一个完全不同的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And then it was sushi. And it was like it was a totally different world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪如果我喜欢某人 ‪我会在他的脸颊上亲一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}If I like someone, I'll give them a little kiss on the cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当时我的动作很快 但感觉非常自然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It was quick, but it just felt very natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（保加利亚 索非亚）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪落地后 我和孩子的妈妈 ‪还有孩子 我们上了一辆车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}When we landed, me and the baby's mother and the baby, we went into a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当然 我也会借此机会问一些问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Of course, I take the opportunity to ask some questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪她告诉我他是一个多么棒的父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}She tells me what a wonderful father he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他仍然抚养支持她们 ‪即使他们已经不在一起了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}that he's still supporting them even though they're not together anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪听到这番话 感觉真的很棒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}which was really, really nice to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们到酒店后登记入住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}When we go to the hotel, we check in,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们一起走进电梯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and when we're walking into the elevator together,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪就在门要关上的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}exactly when the door closes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他搂着我的腰 看着我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}he takes me around the waist and he just looks at me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪把我拉过去给了我一个吻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and he draws me in and just gives me this kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我当时心想 “靠 心里小鹿乱撞）”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and I was like, "Oh, shit," you know, the kind of butterflies...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那动作充满激情 那是你能拥有的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It was passionate, and was just the perfect first kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪最完美的初吻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}that you could have, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪-你们一起睡了 ‪-我们一起睡了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}-You sleep together? -We sleep together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪后来我看到他背上有一些痕迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And then, later on, I could see that he has some marks on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我当时问 我在抚摸的地方 ‪这是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was just wondering, like, what is this? Where, like, I was touching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后他说 “好吧）”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And then he was kind of like, "Oh, well..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他并不知道具体该怎么说 但他说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He didn't exactly know how to say it, but it was, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他曾在南非坐过牢 我说 “什么”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}he had been in jail in South Africa. And I was like, "What?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪就再相信我一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Just trust me once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我为什么要那样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Why should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他之前在那里做过一笔交易 而他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He had a deal going on there, and they had
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪背叛 出卖了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}turned their backs against him and betrayed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以他因欺诈罪进了监狱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So he had gone in prison on false pretenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他是无辜的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He was innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为他是犹太人 ‪所以在监狱里受到看粗暴的对待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He had been manhandled in prison because he was Jewish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这个我以为一切都很好的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Here was this guy I thought had everything going for him
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪和我在一起坐在床上 感觉很脆弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}sitting on the bed with me, being really vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪别转移话题 把邮票给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Just give me the stamps.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我爱你 亚当 亚历克斯 彼得）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Oh. Oh, I love you, Adam, Alex, Peter...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这是你想要拯救的一类人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Here's this kind of person that you want to save,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪尤其是因为他背负的责任太多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}especially 'cause he has so much responsibility on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪每个人都指望着他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Everyone is relying on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪仅管我们之间的关系发展得很快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Even though things had gone very quickly with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但当我坐在那里 ‪我感觉和一个人有一种情感上的联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}but when I sit there and I feel an emotional connection with someone
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:14:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他们对我敞开心扉 我就是这样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and they're opening up, that's just how I am as a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他开始接到很多电话 最后他就说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He starts getting a lot of calls, and, in the end, he just says,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“我们太忙了 ‪我觉得你最好还是回家吧”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"We're so busy. I think it's best if you just go back home."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.28,0:14:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪其实我当时有点失望 我有点想）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was a bit disappointed, actually. I was kind of like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我想多陪陪他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I wanted to spend more time with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（英格兰 伦敦）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我回到伦敦后 ‪我以为我们的联系就会消失\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}When I came back to London, I thought the conversation would die out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我没有任何期待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I didn't expect anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我就感觉我只是多认识他了一些 ‪但我并没有真正“了解他”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I felt like I knew him more, but I didn't really "know him" know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪比如我有多特别 我感觉很特别 ‪但他一走 谁知道呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Like, how special was I? I felt special, but, like, when he leaves, you never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（希望你可以有一点点想我）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我心里在期待 我当时真的希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was hoping. I was really hoping
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他会回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}that he was gonna come back.
