Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我真的很喜欢你）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.36,0:15:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但接着就开始互发信息问候早上好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}But then kept going with, like, good morning messages to each other
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪晚安 还进行视频通话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and good night messages, and FaceTime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（维也纳柏悦酒店）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他就一直在跟我说他去了什么地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He was, like, tagging me where he was going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我也想去维也纳 看起来好漂亮）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当我在工作的时候 ‪你可以听到手机的响声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}When I was at work, you could hear the pinging in your phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪心里想 “我希望是他发来的消息”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and it was, like, "I hope that it's him."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他突然问我 “你的地址是哪儿”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He just suddenly asked me, "So what's your address?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我从来没有收到过这样的花束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Never, ever received a bouquet like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我激动得都哭了）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪想你 想和你待在一起） ‪亲亲你 抱抱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Miss you. Wanna spend some time together... Kiss you, hug you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪感觉我们之间有特别的感情 ‪他也是这么对我说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Feel like we have something special, and he says so to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以我就感觉 “靠 ‪这就是真爱吗”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So I'm kind of like, "Oh, shit. Is this it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（谷歌地图 伦敦公园路四季酒店）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（欢迎回来）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（来酒店）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪能再次见到他真是太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Ah, it was so nice seeing him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我都无法向别人描述这种感觉 ‪就是你真的很想见某个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I can't even describe to someone. Like, when you really want to see someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪感觉你是他的女朋友 ‪这是最好的感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Just feeling that you're his girl is like the best feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.76,0:16:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我就是想尽快再见到你）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我也是）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我们在一起很可爱）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（是的 没错 亲爱的）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但后来就很难见到他了 ‪因为他经常出差\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}But then it was difficult to meet up with him. He was traveling a lot for business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我准备回我在奥斯陆的家 ‪然后我在想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was going home to Oslo and I was thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“你可以来奥斯陆”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"Well, you can come to Oslo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他这样说过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And that was one of the things he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“但宝贝 我在奥斯陆没有任何事可做 ‪那里没有我的生意”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"But, babe, I don't have anything to do in Oslo. There's no business,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我当时非常想他 ‪我当时说 “我再也见不到你了”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and I was missing him so much, I was like, "I'm never gonna be able to see you."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（在线）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（输入中））
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我现在在奥斯陆）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（奥斯陆 欧陆酒店）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你在开玩笑吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}You're kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你是个那么忙的人 ‪然后你决定乘坐私人飞机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}You're such a busy guy, and you decide to take a private jet
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪在凌晨三点抵达这里 来这里看我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and land at like 3:00 a.m. to come and see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪于是我去了他的酒店 ‪还给他买了个情人节礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So I go to his hotel. I bought him, like, a Valentine's present.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那是一本关于和一个挪威人社交的书\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It was a book about having a relationship with a Norwegian.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.88,0:17:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后我写了十件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And then I had made, like, ten things about him
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪让他很棒的事 都是我自己写的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}that makes him wonderful, which I'd written myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后他就问我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And then he just asked me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“我对你的感情很认真 ‪你想成为我的女朋友吗”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"I am serious about you. Do you want to be my girlfriend?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我就感觉 “天啊” ‪这正是你想听到的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And I'm kind of like, "Oh, shit." The kind of words that you wanted to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪对 然后我们就在一起了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Yeah. And then we were together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后他说如果我们能在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}That's when he said there was something he wants to tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他想告诉我一些事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}if we're gonna be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪对他的生活开诚布公\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It was better to be open and honest about how his life was
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪比隐瞒着要好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}than to keep it hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他只是说他需要完成一件大事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He was just talking about this big deal that he needed to get done,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这笔交易价值七千万美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and the deal was worth $70 million,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但钻石行业是个危险的行业\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}but the diamond industry is a dangerous business.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他的安保受到了威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He had these threats surrounding his security.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他在以色列有一个安保团队 ‪彼得好像就是团队的头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He had a security team in Israel. Peter was like the head of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪威胁越来越严重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Threats had gotten worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他给我看了一些照片 ‪比如他们邮箱里收到了子弹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He showed me pictures of, like, they had gotten bullets in the mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.52,0:18:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪有人送了葬礼上的花圈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Funeral flowers had been sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他在特拉维夫的一间公寓装有监控\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He had CCTV of an apartment in Tel Aviv.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪有人闯进来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He had a break-in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪安保团队告诉他 他在伦敦不再安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The security team told him that he wasn't safe in London anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这段时间 他需要躲得远远的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and for time being he needed to stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当然 我非常替他害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Of course, I get super scared for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我可以看出来这让他很紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I could just see that it was straining on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他只是想让我理解 一切都会没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He just wanted my understanding that things were gonna be fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们会在一起的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and we were going to be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我说 “好吧 我会陪着你”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And I was like, "Okay. I'll be here for you."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（英国 伦敦）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我回到家的时候 我的一位朋友 ‪谷歌到了列维耶夫的家族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}When I got back home, one of my friends Googled the Leviev family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（列维耶夫钻石）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（谷歌搜索）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（全球富豪榜第782位 ‪资产16亿美元）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪在非洲有自己的钻石矿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪她说那是最强大的家族之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}She says this is one of the most powerful families.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他们能做大是有原因的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}They've become big for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（弗拉基米尔·普京） ‪是“真正的朋友”）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪对他所参与的事 需要现实一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Need to be realistic about what he's involved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我好久没见到他了 ‪当然让你有点害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I hadn't seen him in a while. And of course it made you a bit scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪于是我检查了他的Tinder ‪看看他在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So I check his Tinder to see where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我看到他在另一个国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I see that he's in a different country.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我还看到他的几张照片有改动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And I also see a couple of his pictures had changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我的心都沉了下来 ‪这意味着他最近很活跃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}My heart just sank, you know, 'cause that means that he's been active.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我很害怕受伤）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我不再用Tinder了 ‪我删除了应用程序 我删除了账户\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm not using Tinder anymore. I deleted the app. I deleted the account.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.36,0:20:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他说我们是一边的 我们是一起的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He tells me that we're a team and we're together
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我没什么好担心的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and that I have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪没有其他人了 只有我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}There's no one else. Only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我在乎你 我想你 ‪一切都会好起来的 宝贝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I care about you. I miss you. And everything will be all right, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我坐下来玩着手机 滑着Tinder\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was sitting by my phone, swiping, swiping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.92,0:20:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪你想要什么样的男生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}What kind of guy were you hoping for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪一个理想的人 要聪明 ‪而且很有趣 很冲动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}An ideal guy. A smart one. And funny. And very impulsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.08,0:21:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（瑞典 斯德哥尔摩）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我是一个非常独立的女人 ‪我一直都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm a very independent woman. I always have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我从16岁开始就是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I've done that since the age of 16,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以我不需要一位照顾我的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}so I don't need a man to take care of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但是我很愿意和一位男士 ‪来共享我的人生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}but I would appreciate to have a man to share my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（佩妮拉 31岁 ‪想和一位让我笑的人分享我的冒险）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我的Tinder资料很杂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}My Tinder profile was a mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪上面有我穿工作装的照片 ‪也有旅行的照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It had some pictures with me dressed for work, traveling,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为我还是希望吸引一位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}because I still wanted to attract this person
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪和我有着同样生活的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}that was living the same life as I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我当时在滑 然后这个人出现了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So I was swiping. And then this guy comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这是个经常旅行的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}This is someone who is well-traveled.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.68,0:21:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪而且工作很努力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And still works very hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以我想 “好极了 我们往右滑吧”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So I thought, "Oh, great. Let's swipe right on that."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（配对成功）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.36,0:22:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我收到了一个配对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I got a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.72,0:22:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（最近的Instagram相册）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他在瑞典做生意 ‪但上面说他住在阿姆斯特丹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He was here in Stockholm for business, but it said he was living in Amsterdam.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他给我发私信问我要不要来看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He texts me and asks me if I want to come visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.80,0:22:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（西蒙·列维耶夫 语音信息）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪明天上午9点有一班飞机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}There is a flight tomorrow at nine o'clock in the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.28,0:22:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪从瑞典飞往阿姆斯特丹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}from Stockholm to Amsterdam.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.84,0:22:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪所以可以的话请告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So tell me if it's all right for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.08,0:22:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他要了我的护照信息 帮我订了机票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He asked about my passport details, booked my flight ticket,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我觉得这是一个很友好的态度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}which I thought was a nice gesture.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.04,0:22:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我从LLD钻石公司的 ‪西蒙·列维耶夫那里收到确认信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I get this confirmation from Simon Leviev at LLD Diamonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.24,0:22:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（谷歌搜索 LLD钻石公司）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.28,0:22:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当然 我开始谷歌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Of course, I started to Google,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.36,0:22:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为你在和任何人约会前 ‪都会在谷歌上搜索他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}because you always Google everyone you're supposed to go on a date with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.44,0:22:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（关于我们）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.12,0:22:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他父亲是钻石大亨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}His father is this diamond tycoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:22:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我就想 “我的天 又一个钻石男”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and I'm just thinking, "Oh my God, another diamond guy."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.96,0:23:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Um... -Another diamond guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.00,0:23:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪又一个钻石男
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.00,0:23:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.92,0:23:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我以前和一个钻石行业的人交往过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I used to date a guy that was in the diamond industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.96,0:23:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪好吧 也许要有第二次了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Okay, maybe second time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（荷兰 阿姆斯特丹）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我坐车去他家 附近的社区非常迷人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I take a car to his house, which is in this lovely, lovely neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他过来打开门了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He comes and opens up the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他穿得很优雅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He dresses very elegantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“对我来说有点矮” ‪这是我的第一个想法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"A little bit short for my taste," was the first thing I was thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.28,0:23:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但是和他聊天很轻松\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}but he's really easy to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.92,0:23:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪很少刚见到某人 ‪就能有这种立刻的共鸣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It's quite rare that you meet someone and you have this instant connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们在共处了一个小时后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}After we spent an hour together,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.64,0:23:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们感觉我们彼此已经认识十年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}we felt like we had known each other for ten years or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.96,0:23:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们去吃了午餐 全体员工欢迎我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We go for lunch, the entire staff welcomes us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.84,0:23:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他们带来了餐厅 ‪专门为西蒙准备的鱼子酱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}They bring a special order of caviar that the restaurant uses just for Simon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.56,0:24:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我觉得上菜好像永远不会停一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I don't think the food ever stopped coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.84,0:24:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他真的问了很多问题 ‪也真的愿意倾听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He really asked a lot of questions, really wanted to listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.24,0:24:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我很欣赏这一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}which I really appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.88,0:24:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为你很少能找到愿意倾听的男人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}'Cause it's quite rare to have men listen sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.60,0:24:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪之后 我们在阿姆斯特丹散步了很久 ‪我看到一个钻石博物馆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Afterwards, we had a nice, long walk around Amsterdam. I see a diamond museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.32,0:24:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我喜欢博物馆 ‪如果你想逛钻石博物馆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I love museums, and if you should go to a diamond museum,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.12,0:24:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你最好和懂行的人一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}you should go with someone in the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.28,0:24:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他知道所有的钻石矿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He knows all about the mines,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.76,0:24:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪怎么切割 哪里有最好的钻石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}how to cut them, where you get the best diamonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.16,0:24:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他什么都知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He knows everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.96,0:24:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪在那之后 他对我做了一点小动作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}After that, he makes this little bit of a move on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.24,0:24:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但感觉不太对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}But it just doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.24,0:24:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他就说 “不行 也许不行 ‪最好还是当朋友吧”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He's like, "No, maybe no. Just... Better just stay friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.80,0:24:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“是啊 也许你说得对”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"Yeah, maybe you're right."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.48,0:24:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪就算我们之间没有浪漫的火花\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Even though there wasn't a romantic energy between us,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.96,0:25:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我也真的很享受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I really enjoyed myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.60,0:25:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（哈哈哈 真的让我很开心）
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.80,0:25:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我一两天后就开始想他了 ‪因为我们玩得很开心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I actually missed him after just a day or two, because we did have a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.76,0:25:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（太奇怪了 我真的很想你）
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.88,0:25:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（我也想你）
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.72,0:25:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们在聊天 打电话 发短信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We were talking and calling and texting.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.56,0:25:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他出去吃饭的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}When he's out to dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.08,0:25:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他会给我发图片 我们会发语音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}he sends me a picture, and we used voice notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.60,0:25:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪很漂亮 很好看 佩妮拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Beautiful looking. Beautiful, Pernilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.32,0:25:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪很高兴明天就能见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Happy to see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.60,0:25:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪有时候你可以有两种不同的人格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}You can be two different types of personalities sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.44,0:25:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以你要么是充电的 要么是耗电的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So either you can be a battery charger or a battery drainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.72,0:25:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪好好工作 好好玩耍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Work hard, play hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.04,0:25:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他绝对是我的充电器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And he was definitely my battery charger.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.72,0:25:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪太好看了 漂亮的裙子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Amazing. Amazing. Beautiful dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.00,0:25:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪有一次我记得 ‪他飞过来就为了和我喝杯咖啡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Once, I remember, like, he flew over just to have a coffee with me one day
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.48,0:25:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为我那天过得很糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}because I was having a bad day.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.40,0:26:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪佩妮拉<i>‪ </i>‪大概十点的时候 ‪我们去喝了一杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Pernilla, about 10 o'clock we're going for a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.76,0:26:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后 十二点半 我们去了俱乐部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Then, 12:30, we're going to the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.56,0:26:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我等不及要见你了 宝贝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Can't wait to see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.44,0:26:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我在他备注旁边加了个王子的表情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I gave him a little bit of a prince emoji next to his name,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.08,0:26:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为有时他的举止就像王子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}because that's how he's behaving sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.84,0:26:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我总是开这个玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And I always make a joke about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.40,0:26:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（你有一件印着王子的衬衫吗 ‪很适合你）
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.08,0:26:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪真的觉得我们有特殊的联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Really felt like we had a special connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.32,0:26:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（英国 伦敦）
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.40,0:26:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我等不及要见你了 ‪我全心全意爱你 我好想你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I can't wait to see you. I love you with all my heart. I miss you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.80,0:26:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙经常出差 ‪我们每天都在聊天 发短信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon was away a lot on business. We'd talk and text every single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.56,0:26:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你的女孩终于完成了今晚的瑜伽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Your girl is finally done with yoga for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.28,0:26:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪她在家做了一些美味的三文鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And she's at home making some delicious salmon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.40,0:26:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我觉得很特别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I felt special.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.60,0:26:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（天啊 谢谢你宝贝）
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.00,0:26:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪感觉太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It was just amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.92,0:27:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后 他问我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And then, he asked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.16,0:27:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（搬来和我一起住）
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.96,0:27:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（很乐意）
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.92,0:27:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这是最好的感觉 你懂的 当有人和你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It's just the best feeling, you know, when you have someone
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.00,0:27:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪保持在一个频道上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and both are on the same wavelength.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.00,0:27:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪该去二号公寓了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Time for apartment number two.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.96,0:27:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪客厅可以看电影什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Living room where we can watch movies and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.60,0:27:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我梦想着我们两个人能一起生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was dreaming of how it would be for the two of us to live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.96,0:27:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后有一个很棒的厨房\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And then you have this awesome kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.24,0:27:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这里是卧室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And here is the bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.32,0:27:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙告诉我预算是每个月1.5万美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon tells me that the budget is $15,000 per month.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.40,0:27:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪第三间公寓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Third apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.68,0:27:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以我要去所有这些 ‪漂亮的公寓转一转\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So I'm going all the rounds in these amazing apartments.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.68,0:27:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪有时候西蒙和我还会打视频一起看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And sometimes I even have Simon with me on FaceTime.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.84,0:28:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这是我和他一个很好的联系方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It was just a really nice way to connect with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.32,0:28:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪就算他不在这 我们也能一起完成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}even though he wasn't there, to do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.64,0:28:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪可以看到科文特花园广场的景色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The view is out to the Piazza at Covent Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.48,0:28:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我订了公寓）
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.52,0:28:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（太棒了 亲爱的 太感谢你了）
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.20,0:28:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（等不及和你一起生活了）
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.00,0:28:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪塞西莉 亲爱的 我爱你 我想你 ‪我等不及要见你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Cecilie, my love, I love you, I miss you. I can't wait to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.44,0:28:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（照片）
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.48,0:28:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（血）
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.24,0:28:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（彼得受伤了）
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.28,0:28:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪半夜的时候 我收到彼得的照片 ‪他是西蒙的保镖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}In the middle of the night, I get a picture of Peter, Simon's bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.36,0:28:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙发过来“彼得受伤了” ‪我在想“怎么回事”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon is writing "Peter hurt," and I'm like, "What the fuck?"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.88,0:29:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（什么）
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.12,0:29:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（发生了什么）
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.72,0:29:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪好吧 就是今晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Well, this is the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.96,0:29:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你能写你的名字吗 ‪当然 我也可以帮你写\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Can you write your first name? Or I can write it, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.88,0:29:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们在救护车里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We're in an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.04,0:29:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你能写吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Can you write that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.16,0:29:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他说 “他们在追我 感谢彼得”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He just says that, "They were going after me. Thank God for Peter."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.00,0:29:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“如果不是他 我就死定了”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"If not, I would be dead."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.80,0:29:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪没关系 亲爱的 没关系 ‪我跟你说了我们在打仗 我们要坚强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It's okay, love. It's okay. I told you, we're in a war. We need to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.44,0:29:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我不知道该怎么办 ‪他说 “我们现在安全了”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I didn't know what to do. And he just says, "We're safe now."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.72,0:29:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“我们有人照顾了 你只需要去睡觉”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"We're being taken care of. You just need to sleep."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.20,0:29:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪第二天早上 西蒙给我发了个语音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The next morning, Simon sends me a voice note.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.88,0:29:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为当时的情况 涉及安全什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Because of the situation, with the security and everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.76,0:29:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他们不允许我用我的信用卡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}they told me I'm not allowed to use my credit card.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.24,0:29:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他不能使用他的信用卡了 ‪因为他的安保团队说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He can't use his cards anymore because the security team has said his enemies
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.80,0:29:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他的敌人正在根据 ‪他的信用卡消费记录来定位他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}are tracing his spending and where he is based on his credit card use.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.56,0:29:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我想请你帮个忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I wanted to ask you a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.64,0:30:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪如果你有美国运通信用卡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}If you have an American Express credit card,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.88,0:30:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我可以把它关联到我的账户\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I can link it to my account.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.68,0:30:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他只是想问问 ‪他能不能借我的信用卡用一段时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He was just wondering if he could use my cards for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.56,0:30:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这会对他帮助很大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It would just help him a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.04,0:30:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪只是暂时的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It's just temporary, like, for, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.96,0:30:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪大概两周左右吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}two weeks or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.00,0:30:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我是他的女朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.28,0:30:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他当然会问我 你相信我 我也相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Of course he would ask me. Like, you trust me and I trust you,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.28,0:30:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以我们当然会互相帮助 ‪这根本不是问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}so of course we're gonna help each other. It wasn't even a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.28,0:30:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪白金美国运通卡在我的名下 ‪他像说过的一样开始使用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The Platinum Amex is in my name, and he starts using it as he said he would,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.00,0:30:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但他很快就到限额了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}but he maxes out quite quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.52,0:30:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以他直接向美国证券所付款 ‪我收到了收据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So he makes payment directly to Amex, and I get the receipt from him,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.80,0:30:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他说钱就在路上 但与此同时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and he says that the money is on the way, but in the meantime,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.36,0:30:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他想让我去阿姆斯特丹 ‪给他带2.5万美元的现金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}he wants me to come to Amsterdam and bring some cash to him. $25,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.72,0:30:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（如果不能按时付清怎么办 ‪不理解我们为什么需要现金））
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.80,0:31:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（无法追踪）
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.20,0:31:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我怎么能弄到这么多现金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}How on Earth am I going to get that amount of cash?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.12,0:31:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（快捷贷款）
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.08,0:31:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我借了一笔贷款 取出了一些现金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I took out a loan, which I then took out in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.80,0:31:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪包里有那么多现金 我当时吓坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was super scared having that amount of cash in my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.40,0:31:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪尤其是我们通过安检的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Especially when we went through security.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.52,0:31:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我当时压力很大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was super stressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.76,0:31:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪如果他们对钱有任何疑问 ‪我该怎么解释\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}How was I gonna explain the money if I got any questions about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.56,0:31:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（荷兰 阿姆斯特丹）
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.28,0:31:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我见到他的那一刻 就有安全感了 ‪我最大的问题就是和他分开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The moment I'm with him, I feel safe. My biggest issue was being apart from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.12,0:31:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他真的对我很感激\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He was really grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.08,0:32:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他说我所做的一切都是为了他的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He told me that everything I was doing is keeping him safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.00,0:32:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但几个小时后 ‪安保团队称出现了问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}But within hours, the security team said there was a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.76,0:32:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪出于安全考虑 ‪他删除了自己的Instagram\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He deletes his Instagram because of security measures,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.92,0:32:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后他让我把我的账户 ‪也设为私密账户\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and then he asked me to make my account private.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.52,0:32:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪全都清除掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Take it all away.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.16,0:32:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他说他们可以通过他 来找到我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He says that they can come and get me through him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.80,0:32:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当然我会变得很多疑 ‪这到底是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Of course, I get paranoid. What the fuck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.44,0:32:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪后来 西蒙接到了一个电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Later on, Simon gets a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.48,0:32:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他跟彼得打电话 并打开了免提 ‪他说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He puts Peter on the speakerphone, and he says,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.24,0:32:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“西蒙 出现了一个安全漏洞 ‪他们知道你在哪儿”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"Simon, there's been a security breach. They know where you are."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.24,0:32:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“飞机准备起飞了 我不能告诉你 ‪你要去的地方”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"The plane is ready to leave. I can't tell you where you're going."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.84,0:32:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪彼得问他是否可以把公寓里的灯关掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Peter is asking if he can please turn off the lights in the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.88,0:32:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我当时害怕极了 ‪他们现在要来了吗 我们锁门了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm shit scared. Are they coming now? Did we lock the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.16,0:33:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪看到你在乎的人身处险境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Just seeing someone that you care so much for in danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.32,0:33:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪而且你可以看到他的精神状况不太好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and, like, you can see that he was not doing well mentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.40,0:33:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我能看出他很纠结\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I could see that he was struggling so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.56,0:33:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪最后 他只告诉我 他必须要走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And in the end, he just told me that he had to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.00,0:33:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他一着陆 就把位置发给了我 ‪他抵达了斯德哥尔摩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}When he lands, he sends me the geotag. He's landed in Stockholm.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.96,0:33:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（瑞典 斯德哥尔摩）
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.12,0:33:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他来这里了 非常心血来潮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He is here. Very spontaneous.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.32,0:33:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以我问他）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So I ask him...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.56,0:33:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（你今晚有什么计划）
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.84,0:33:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（派对）
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.04,0:33:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪俱乐部基本上是一片充满女人的海洋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The club is basically an ocean with women,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.24,0:33:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪或者我管她们叫香槟女郎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}or as I call them, champagne girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.68,0:33:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪她们基本就像是苍蝇一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}They are basically like flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.52,0:33:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你放一个烂香蕉出来 ‪苍蝇就会围过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Like, you put out a rotten banana, and they just attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.24,0:34:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但这些女孩看到香槟时也会这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}but these girls do the same thing when they see a bottle of champagne.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.40,0:34:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙当然要为整个闹场买单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And Simon is of course paying for this entire circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.72,0:34:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他用现金支付 ‪就为了确保每个人都玩得开心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He's paying with cash and just making sure that everyone is having a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.92,0:34:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他们都喝得酩酊大醉 ‪尤其是西蒙的保镖彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}All of them are quite drunk, especially Simon's bodyguard, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.80,0:34:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这不是我想要参与的环境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}This is not an environment that I want to be in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.76,0:34:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以我就待了10到15分钟 然后说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So I just stay for 10, 15 minutes and then just say,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.40,0:34:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“我们明天再聊吧 ‪祝你们今晚玩儿得开心”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"Let's talk tomorrow and enjoy your night and have fun."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.80,0:34:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪第二天早上 ‪我发短信问他宿醉怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The morning after, I text him and ask how the hangover is
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.92,0:34:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪并问他如果想喝杯咖啡 ‪我们就去喝一杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and maybe if he needs a cup of coffee, we should go for one,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.40,0:34:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后他立马回复了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and then he texts me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.08,0:34:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他已经在西班牙了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He's already in Spain.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.28,0:35:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（你怎么时候结束 宝贝 ‪卡又不能用了）
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.44,0:35:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（请给他们打电话 我现在在酒店）
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.80,0:35:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪运通卡是我的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The Amex card is in my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.24,0:35:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（美国运通）
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.20,0:35:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（今天我们能为您做些什么吗）
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.16,0:35:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（呼叫人工客服）
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.32,0:35:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪欢迎致电美国运通\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Welcome to American Express.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.20,0:35:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以我不得不假装 ‪我是那个四处旅行的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So I had to pretend that I was the one traveling around, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.48,0:35:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我知道你的卡不能用了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I understand your card isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.76,0:35:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我帮您联系能帮助您的人 说或输入）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'll connect you with someone who can assist. Say or enter...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.08,0:35:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我需要知道他到底花了多少钱 ‪住在哪家酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I needed to know exactly the amount that he was spending, which hotel he was in,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.12,0:35:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这样他们就会相信是我在用那张卡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}so they would believe that I was the one using the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.32,0:35:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们需要走了 我们需要旅行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We need to go. We need to travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.20,0:35:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这让事情变得很复杂 亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It's making things very complicated, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.08,0:35:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪几个小时后他再次打来 ‪卡又被禁用了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Couple of hours later he would call again, and it's blocked again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.24,0:35:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪欢迎致电美国运通\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Welcome to American Express.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.40,0:35:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后我需要打电话给美国运通\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Then I need to call Amex,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.96,0:35:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙已经告诉了我会发生这种事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and Simon had already told me that this would happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.64,0:35:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这是我一开始就需要做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}that it would be something that I would need to do at the start
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.88,0:35:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪打电话给他们并解决问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}to call them and fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.36,0:36:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（卡又可以用了 什么情况）
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.84,0:36:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪另一个问题是信用卡额度不够\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The other problem was that the credit limit wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.56,0:36:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们必须让卡能用 让他能用信用卡 ‪因为他有一整个团队要养\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We had to get it up so he could spend it, 'cause he had an entire team, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.76,0:36:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪于是我说 “好吧 ‪但你现在打算怎么做呢”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So I was like, "Okay, but how are you going to do that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.32,0:36:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他说 “我可以雇用你”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He said, "Well, I can employ you."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.96,0:36:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（LLD钻石公司）
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.72,0:36:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（联系方式）
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.64,0:36:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后他打电话给LLD钻石公司的人 ‪问我护照的详细信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He then calls someone in LLD Diamonds and asks for my passport details,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.60,0:36:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这样我就可以被录入就职登记系统了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}so I can be put into the employment registry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.44,0:36:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（发送）
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.12,0:36:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（发送中））
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.52,0:36:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我只是想说 ‪“我并不是真正在那里工作”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I just tried to say, "Well, I am not really working there."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.84,0:36:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他说 “你在这里工作 我是总裁 ‪如果他们打电话来 你就是被雇用了”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He's like, "Well, you are. I'm the CEO. If they call, you are employed."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.76,0:36:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪如果不是大事 ‪我是不会向你要任何东西的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I would never ask you for anything if it was not serious shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.28,0:36:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所有这些安全问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}All these security issues,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.96,0:36:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你一直在我身边 ‪所以谢谢你 亲爱的 我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}you've always been there for me, so thank you, my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.12,0:36:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们当时正处于危机之中 ‪不然我们还能做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We were in a crisis at this point. Like, what else are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.84,0:36:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（列维耶夫集团公司）
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.40,0:36:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后我就被雇用了 ‪我还收到了工资单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So then I got employed. I got pay slips.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.40,0:37:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪-多少钱 ‪-赚得非常多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}-How much? -Earning so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.20,0:37:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我记得大概是每月九万四千美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I think it was, like, $94,000 per month.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.20,0:37:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我发这个单子给工作人员 ‪来证明我赚得这么多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I send this over to prove that I earn much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.36,0:37:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这就能让他们像这样提高信用限额\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}That makes them raise the credit limit like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.92,0:37:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当然 你还是有点担心的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Of course, you are a bit worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.96,0:37:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（电汇明细及收据）
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.00,0:37:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但他给我发了一张瑞士信贷的收据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}but he sends me a receipt from Credit Suisse
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.04,0:37:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他直接通过那里向我转账\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}where he's making a transfer directly to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.12,0:37:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪转了25万美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It's for $250,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.68,0:37:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这笔钱用于抵消他花的钱绰绰有余\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It's more than enough to pay for the amount that he was spending.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.92,0:37:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（一切都没事 别担心 亲爱的 ‪一切都会没事的）
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.88,0:37:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（一切都在掌控之中）
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.96,0:37:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（希腊 米科诺斯岛）
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.48,0:37:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪米科诺斯岛就像一个完美的游乐场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Mykonos is like a perfect playground.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.04,0:37:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你会看到很多游艇 ‪很多名人 很多模特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}You will see a lot of yachts, a lot of celebrities, a lot of models.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.56,0:37:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你也会为白天的派对 ‪准备好你所有的比基尼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}You pack all your bikinis, definitely, for the daytime parties as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.60,0:38:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我和西蒙打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I am on the phone with Simon,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.28,0:38:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他告诉我他刚认识了他的新女友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and he tells me he has just met his new girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.72,0:38:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪宝丽娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Polina.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.00,0:38:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我让他在米科诺斯岛和我们会合 ‪他照做了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I tell him they should meet us in Mykonos, and he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.76,0:38:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（挪威 奥斯陆）
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.28,0:38:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当时我正要去奥斯陆 ‪去见我的朋友 我的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was going to Oslo. To see my friends, see my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.72,0:38:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪而且我真的很想向他们介绍他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And I really wanted to introduce him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.60,0:38:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我就一直等着他 ‪他说他第二天就过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm just waiting for him. He said he was gonna come the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.64,0:38:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那是我第一次见到宝丽娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I meet Polina for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.96,0:38:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪她是那种典型的俄罗斯模特 ‪非常年轻 但她很务实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}She's this typical, like, Russian model. Quite young. But she's very down to earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.56,0:38:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我真的很喜欢她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And I really liked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.44,0:38:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他似乎被她深深迷住了 ‪他们看起来很般配\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He seems very smitten over her. They seemed like a good match.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.16,0:38:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪听着 我现在过不去了 我过不去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Look, I cannot come right now. I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.52,0:38:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪安保团队留住了他 “你需要远离”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The security team had told him, "You need to stay away."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.00,0:39:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我感到非常失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I felt deeply disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.92,0:39:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但最重要的是确保他的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}But what's most important is actually to keep him safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.08,0:39:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当然 他已经预定了 ‪带私人游泳池的豪华套房\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Of course he had booked the grand suite, with own private pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.52,0:39:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那个房间大约一晚五千美元 ‪非常豪华\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It's about $5,000 a night, this room. It's absolutely gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.56,0:39:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我知道你不愿意给银行打电话 ‪但有时这是必要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I know you hate to ring up the bank, but sometimes it is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.00,0:39:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪需要为团队其他成员订几张票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I need to book some tickets for the rest of the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.16,0:39:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪突然需要为整个团队弄到这么多钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Suddenly need to get so much money for this entire team
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.84,0:39:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他们坐着商务舱 吃着昂贵的晚餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}that is traveling business class, that is having expensive dinners.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.68,0:39:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪感觉就是他们和客户出去 ‪花费达到了一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Like, they're going out with clients, and the spend is to another level
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.52,0:39:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你从未见过的水平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}that you have never, ever seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.08,0:39:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这是我一直在做的事 ‪就是开会 不停地开会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}This is what I do all the time. Just meetings and more meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.16,0:39:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪两万美元是一笔大数目 ‪他们三天就花光了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}$20,000 is a lot of money, and that was spent in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.68,0:40:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙问 ‪“我们现在要去哪儿 做什么”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon asks, "Where should we go now?"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.52,0:40:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们决定去糖果俱乐部 ‪也被称为亿万富翁俱乐部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We decide to go to Bonbonniere, also known as the billionaire's club.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.72,0:40:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你不付卡座的钱是进不来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}You don't get in here without paying for a table,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.36,0:40:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪卡座低消通常是两千美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}which is normally $2,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.64,0:40:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪对这里的人来说 这点钱微不足道 ‪就是喝个咖啡的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}For people here, this is peanuts for them. This is coffee money.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.92,0:40:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（无法支付 请换卡支付）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.04,0:40:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他又刷爆了信用卡 ‪所以他告诉我去申请更多贷款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He maxes out the credit card again. So he told me to get more loans.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.64,0:40:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我就是有点害怕 ‪需要承担这么多的贷款）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.36,0:40:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪别担心 我会完成这笔交易的 ‪我需要支付香槟的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Don't worry, I will finish this deal. Champagne's on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.24,0:40:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙点了几瓶香槟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon orders in a couple of bottles of champagne.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.12,0:40:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们还没来得及凑钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Before we even have time to try and chip in,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.88,0:40:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他就已经付了帐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}he has already paid for the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.44,0:40:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙很慷慨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon is very generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.52,0:40:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（尽量获得更多的贷款或现金）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.56,0:40:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我会补偿你的 我保证）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.44,0:40:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我又借贷了四万美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I take out a loan for $40,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.00,0:41:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙和宝丽娜还在继续他们 ‪小小的夏季旅行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon and Polina were continuing their little summer tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.36,0:41:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我想再做一笔交易 但没成功\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I tried to do, like, another transaction, and it didn't go through.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.80,0:41:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪每隔两天或三天就有一个新的请求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Every second or third day is a new request.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.92,0:41:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我需要 尽快）
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.56,0:41:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪先是法国 然后他们去了维也纳 ‪他们还去了瑞士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}France, and then they were going Vienna. They were going Switzerland.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.52,0:41:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪差不多了 我已经完成交易的97%了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Almost there. I'm 97% done with the deals.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.00,0:41:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪每次他刷爆信用卡 ‪我就必须去申请新的贷款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Each time he maxes out the card, I have to take out a new loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.40,0:41:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪易通宝银行五万美元 挪威银行 ‪1.25万美元 信用卡一万美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}$50,000 Instabank. $12,500 DNB. $10,000 for a credit card.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.84,0:41:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（意大利 罗马）
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.96,0:41:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“我们在罗马见吧 ‪我们需要去看看斗兽场”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"Let's meet up in Rome. We need to go and see the Coliseum."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.32,0:41:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.12,0:41:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.56,0:41:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这辆神奇的劳斯莱斯幻影 ‪带我们参观了所有著名景点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}This amazing Rolls-Royce Phantom is taking us around all the famous sites,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.28,0:41:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪比如西班牙阶梯 斗兽场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}like the Spanish Stairs, the Coliseum,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.00,0:41:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪去许愿池扔几枚硬币\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}the Trevi Fountain to throw a few pennies.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.68,0:42:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我的生活确实需要更多的运气 ‪看看这能不能解决问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I definitely need some more luck in my life. Let's see if this can sort it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.12,0:42:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪检查一下这张卡的情况 ‪就现在 这很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Check what is going on with the card. Now. It's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.72,0:42:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他答应给我的钱还没有到我的账上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Money he had promised me still hasn't come into my account.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.76,0:42:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我希望今天或明天钱能转过来））
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.36,0:42:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我已经做过了 所以现在不重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I've already done it so it doesn't matter right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.96,0:42:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪对于目前的情况 ‪我们现在需要一个解决方案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We need a solution right now for the current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.96,0:42:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这是一种我从未经历过的压力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It's kind of like a pressure that I have never experienced before
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.60,0:42:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪让别人的生活取决于你所做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}to have someone's life depending on what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.64,0:42:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我正面临着安全威胁 有人想杀我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}You know, I'm facing security threats with people trying to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.44,0:42:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪如果他不能用那张卡 ‪出了什么问题 那他就有危险了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}If he couldn't use the card, if something went wrong, he could be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.12,0:42:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪如果我不帮他 会发生什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And if I didn't help him, what might happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.84,0:42:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（未接来电）
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.60,0:42:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪早上好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.64,0:42:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你为我做的事 我们一起经历的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The things you're doing for me, the things we're going through together,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.96,0:42:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪都是为了生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}it's for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.92,0:42:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这让我明白 你就是我的命中注定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}This is what is making me see that you are the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.16,0:42:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪独家银行两万美元 ‪北欧联合银行一万五千美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}$20,000, Monobank. $15,000, Nordea.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.00,0:43:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们都给彼此一个大大的拥抱 ‪说我们应该很快再见面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We all give each other a big hug and say that we should meet again soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.16,0:43:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪在这个美妙的夏天之后 真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}after just like an amazing summer, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.16,0:43:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你取出了多少钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}How much had you taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.36,0:43:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪25万美元 这不是我的初衷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}$250,000. That's not what I signed up for.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.60,0:43:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪-很多钱 ‪-是很大一大笔钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}-A lot. -It is a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.68,0:43:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我知道你做了太多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I know you have done, uh, too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.76,0:43:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪为了我 为了我们 为了一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}for me, for us, for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.60,0:43:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我知道你累了 你想和我在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I know you're tired and you want to be together,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.00,0:43:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当然 我也很想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}which, of course, I do want as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.76,0:43:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我明白 但一切都会好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I understand. Everything will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.24,0:43:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我很累 很烦 我就是需要一些钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was getting so tired and annoyed and I just needed some kind of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.12,0:43:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这时他说 “你可以到阿姆斯特丹来 ‪我可以给你一张支票”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}That's when he says, "You can come to Amsterdam and I can give you a check."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.84,0:44:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（荷兰 阿姆斯特丹）
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.24,0:44:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他看起来更冷淡 ‪没有之前那种感情了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He seemed colder. Wasn't the same kind of affection.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.80,0:44:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他的眼睛里似乎有一片乌云 ‪我无法看透\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}There was almost a cloud across his eyes that I couldn't pierce through.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.16,0:44:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当我们进入公寓时 支票已经签好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}When we get into the apartment, the check is already there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.84,0:44:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这张支票比我现在的债务值钱多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The check is worth much more than the debt I have now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.84,0:44:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们想要在一起 ‪但我能感觉到之间有距离\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We're trying to be together. But I can just feel a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.00,0:44:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那晚并不美好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It wasn't a good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.68,0:44:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（英国 伦敦）
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.28,0:44:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我从阿姆斯特丹回来的第一件事 ‪就是把这张支票兑现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The first thing I do when I come back from Amsterdam is cash this check.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.80,0:44:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我真的需要这张支票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I really needed that check to go through.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.68,0:45:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（你的密码）
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.32,0:45:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我有八 九个债主 你知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I had eight, nine creditors, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.56,0:45:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这么多邮件同时传给了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}That's a lot of emails coming down on you at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.28,0:45:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（登陆）
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.72,0:45:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（查看你的账户）
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.00,0:45:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（搜索交易）
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.40,0:45:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（即将到来的款项）
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.08,0:45:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（你目前没有支付）
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.64,0:45:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我每天都在查我的银行账户\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I check my bank account every single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.36,0:45:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（查看你的账户）
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.64,0:45:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（当前余额）
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.92,0:45:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当四天过去了 ‪我知道我需要给银行打电话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}When four days have passed, I just know that I need to call the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.64,0:45:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（帮助并联系我们）
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.80,0:45:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（联系我们）
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.68,0:45:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪有什么能帮您的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}How can I help you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.28,0:45:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪她说 “我们不会兑现”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}She says, "We won't cash it."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.76,0:45:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪而她不能告诉我原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And she couldn't tell me why.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.56,0:45:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当时我正站在那儿打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And that's when I was just standing on the phone, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.40,0:45:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪感觉我呼吸困难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}feeling that I had hard to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.24,0:45:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（正在呼叫西蒙）
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.64,0:45:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪塞西莉 我不明白 我们有）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Cecilie, I don't understand. We have...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.44,0:46:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我在问支票的问题 我说“不好使”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was asking about the check, like, "It didn't work."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.08,0:46:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他说 “好吧 去他妈的 ‪我把钱给了你 所以）”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He says, "Well, fuck it. I gave you the money, so..."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.84,0:46:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“我已经完成了我的责任”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"I did my deal."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.00,0:46:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我已经给过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I already done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.16,0:46:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我这辈子从没听过他这么冷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Never hear him so cold in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.88,0:46:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪就像电话里那个人 ‪已经不再是我的男朋友了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It was like that person on the phone was no longer my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.04,0:46:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪不再是我的男朋友了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Was no longer my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.40,0:46:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪只是一片黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I... It was just a, uh... just a darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.56,0:46:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我知道我的处境很糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I know I was in deep shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.96,0:46:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（收件箱）
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.80,0:46:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（更新 账户停用）
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.12,0:46:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你有九个债主时 你会怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Like, what do you do when you have nine creditors on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.32,0:46:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（这是你的最终通知）
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.56,0:46:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我打了运通卡的服务热线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I called the Amex helpline.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.60,0:46:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他们能听出我有多紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}They can hear how stressed I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.64,0:46:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他们说 “别动 我们会来找你”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}They just said, "Stay put. We will come to you."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.16,0:47:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我很害怕他们会来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was shit scared they were gonna come and handcuff me
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.92,0:47:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪把我拷走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and take me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.16,0:47:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我寄过来的文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The documents that I sent over.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.64,0:47:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我在电话里说的谎话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The lies I told on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.12,0:47:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我把我的卡给了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I gave him my card.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.04,0:47:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我把一切都告诉了他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I tell them everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.28,0:47:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他们说 “你有他的照片吗”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}They said, "Do you have a picture of him?"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.68,0:47:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那一刻他们看着对方说 ‪就是那个男人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}That moment when they look at each other and they say that's the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.04,0:47:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪该死 该死 你知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Fuck. Shit. You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.28,0:47:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“他用了哪种名字” ‪然后我说西蒙·列维耶夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"What kind of name did he use?" And then I said Simon Leviev.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.40,0:47:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他们说 “好吧 这是 ‪他一直用的名字之一”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And they said, "Well, that's one of many names that he's been using."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.52,0:47:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪很多名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"Many names"?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.96,0:47:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪跟我同床共枕的这个人是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Who is this guy I've been sharing the same bed with?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.60,0:47:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“他是专业的 他靠诈骗营生”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"He's a professional. He does this for a living."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.68,0:48:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪一切都是谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Everything's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.88,0:48:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他不是钻石王子 ‪他不是亿万富翁的儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He's not a prince of diamonds. He's not the son of a billionaire.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.72,0:48:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我所爱的男人从来都不是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The man I loved was never real.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.88,0:48:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他伪造了一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He faked everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.64,0:48:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪太可怕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It was horrible, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.00,0:48:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为我依然）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}'Cause I still...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.68,0:48:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪从某种意义上来说 ‪我还是爱他 你知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}In a sense, I still loved him, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.44,0:48:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪或是我以为的那个人 ‪就像是你知道了一切都是假的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Or the person I thought that he was. Like, you know everything is a lie,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.80,0:48:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但你在手机里依然还有这个童话故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}but then you still have this fairy tale that's going on, on your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.36,0:48:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙 后面还有一颗心 ‪因为我无法移掉它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon, with still the heart behind it, 'cause I couldn't remove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.56,0:48:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为我还是希望他是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}'Cause I still wanted him to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.12,0:48:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我不明白怎么会有人这么邪恶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I don't understand how someone can be so fucking evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.56,0:48:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我觉得他懂我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I felt that he knew me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.84,0:49:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他们一走 我就想跟我妈说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The minute they're gone, I want to speak to my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.88,0:49:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（妈妈）
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.36,0:49:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪她只是跟我说 “你需要回家去挪威”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}She just told me, "You need to get back home to Norway."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.64,0:49:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“我需要你跟我在一起”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"I need you to be with me."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.60,0:49:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（挪威 奥斯陆）
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.92,0:49:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我回看了短信里的消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was going through the messages in the text.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.76,0:49:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我还在问 “我们什么时候 ‪能处理好钱的问题”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was still asking, "When are we going to fix the money?"
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.48,0:49:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们两个之间最后的信息是 ‪“我在努力”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The last messages between the two of us is like, "I'm working on it."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.96,0:49:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（拉黑联系人）
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.56,0:49:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（拉黑）
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.96,0:49:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后我拉黑了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And then I blocked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.44,0:49:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪没什么好说的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}There was nothing else to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.36,0:49:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（你拉黑了这个联系人）
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.56,0:49:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那时我记得他有我妈的电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}That's when I remember he has my mom's number.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.88,0:50:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪嘿 你拉黑了我 我不知道是什么原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Hey, you blocked me, I don't know what is your reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.12,0:50:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我在找你 反正你也不想说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm trying to reach you. You don't want to talk anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.20,0:50:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我想告诉你一件事 接受我的建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I want to tell you something. Take my advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.08,0:50:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪小心点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Just watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.84,0:50:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为万事皆有报应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Because with every action there will be a reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.28,0:50:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我超级害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I got super scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.08,0:50:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但我妈妈更害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}But my mom got even more scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.96,0:50:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们打电话给挪威的警察 ‪因为他知道我的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We call the police in Norway, because he knows everything about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.40,0:50:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他有我所有的护照资料 ‪我住的地方 我妈住的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He has all my passport details, where I was living, where my mom is living.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.04,0:50:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他在电话里跟她通过话 ‪他知道我在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He's spoken to her on the phone. He knows where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.40,0:50:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但警方似乎并不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}But the police didn't seem to care.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.32,0:50:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我不知道他有什么能力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I don't know what he is capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.40,0:51:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我已经坐立不安好几天了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I've been on the edge for several days.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.08,0:51:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（美国运通账户明细）
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.88,0:51:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我有这么多债主 ‪我必须让他们每个人都知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I had all these creditors. I had to let them know, each one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.20,0:51:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪不只是两个银行 大概有九个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It wasn't just two banks. There were, like, nine of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.64,0:51:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（支付金额 ‪53万6,583.98挪威克朗）
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.76,0:51:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪这种贷款的利息很高 ‪它们会把我活吞了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}For this kind of loan, the interest is so high, that they would just eat me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.84,0:51:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（欠款）
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.80,0:51:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我觉得自己快淹死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I felt that I was just drowning.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.44,0:51:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪就像是有人把我拖到了水底\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It was like someone was just dragging me to the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.60,0:51:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我在这条路上开着车 ‪看见一个拖车向我开过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was driving down this road, and I saw a trailer coming towards me,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.80,0:51:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我在想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.84,0:51:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“要是我把车开过去呢” 你知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"What if I just take the car over," you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.48,0:51:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后撞上拖车 你知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And just hit... just hit the trailer, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.96,0:51:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那至少就完事了 你知道吗 ‪然后我就害怕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Then at least it's done, you know? And that's when I got scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.72,0:51:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那时我真的很害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}That's when I got really scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.56,0:51:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我把自己送进精神病房 ‪因为我不知道该怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I put myself into a psychiatric ward because I didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.20,0:52:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我在家看到手机开始闪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was at home, and I could see the phone started flashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.84,0:52:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我看到是西蒙 他给我发了新闻报道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I see it's Simon, and he has sent me news articles.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.28,0:52:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（亿万富翁的儿子被卷进 ‪以色列钻石走私案）
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.84,0:52:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪西蒙的父亲会被警方审问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon's father is gonna be questioned by the police
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.20,0:52:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪有关一个大型钻石走私案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}in a big diamond smuggling case.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.16,0:52:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪西蒙家的人被逮捕了 ‪也涉及到俄罗斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Members of Simon's family have gotten arrested. Russia is involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.76,0:52:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我给他打了电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}-I give him a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.92,0:52:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪听起来很可怕）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}That sounds really scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.16,0:52:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他的声音很乱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He sounds all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.28,0:52:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他说警察介入了 ‪他们关了所有账户 所有信用卡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He says police went in. They have shut down all accounts, all credit cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.72,0:52:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪一个办公室里的女孩跳楼自杀了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}One girl in the office literally jumped from the building and killed herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.24,0:53:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（该女子被发现死在））\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}But Simon says he doesn't believe that this lady jumped off a building.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.32,0:53:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他相信是有人进去把她扔了下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He believes that someone went in and threw her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.24,0:53:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们没有别的选择 你知道）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We don't have the options, you know, the...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.80,0:53:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我开始非常害怕 我在想 ‪“到底是怎么回事”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And I'm getting so scared. I'm like, "What is really going on?"
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.56,0:53:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他说现在的安全状况很糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And he says that the security situation right now is really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.44,0:53:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我经历了我人生中最糟糕的一晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I have the worst night in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.16,0:53:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪几天后 我的手机把我吵醒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}A few days later, I can feel my phone buzzing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.52,0:53:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙发了很多信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon is sending a lot of messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.68,0:53:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪天啊 昨晚发生了什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Oh, my God, what happened last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.12,0:53:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪有人试图刺杀我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Someone tried to stab me, and
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.72,0:53:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以彼得的头缝了几针\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}so Peter broke his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.60,0:53:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪天啊 你说有人刺杀你是什么意思 ‪怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Jesus. What do you mean tried to stab you? What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.48,0:53:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙说 “这是我的敌人策划的”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon said, "This is my enemies behind this."
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.84,0:53:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他很担心有人在追杀他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He was really concerned that someone was after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.52,0:53:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（语音信息）
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.72,0:53:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后我收到了他的语音信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And then I get a voice note from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.88,0:53:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我想请你帮个忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I want to ask you, uh, a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.16,0:53:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“佩妮拉 我很不好意思 ‪开口请你帮忙”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"Pernilla, I am really embarrassed to even ask you."
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.24,0:54:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“你可以借我三万美元吗”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"Would it be possible for me to borrow $30,000?"
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.32,0:54:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这对我会有很大 很大的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It would be a huge, huge, huge, huge, huge, huge help.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.52,0:54:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪如果你能帮忙 请告诉我 太谢谢你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Please let me know if you can do something. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.40,0:54:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我没有三万美元可以借\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I didn't have $30,000 to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.20,0:54:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我在妈妈家待了三个月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'd been at my mom's now for three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.48,0:54:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我有存款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I had my savings
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.16,0:54:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但那是我用来给自己买公寓的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}that was gonna go to buy myself a new apartment where I'm supposed to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.36,0:54:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但是 哪一个更重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}But, what is more important,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.24,0:54:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我朋友的安全状况 ‪还是我买间公寓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}my friend's security situation or me buying an apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.00,0:54:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（银行卡号）
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.20,0:54:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪谢谢你为我做的一切）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Thank you for everything you've done...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.04,0:54:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我在和他通电话的时候 ‪进行了银行转账\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And I make a bank transfer while I'm on the phone with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.00,0:54:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他很感谢 ‪有我这么好的朋友可以相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He's really grateful to have such a good friend as me that he really can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.96,0:55:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我躺在精神病院的床上 看着手机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was laying in bed at the psychiatric ward, on my phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.56,0:55:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪回顾和我见面的这些人 ‪经历的更多细节\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}going through more details with the people that I had met.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.24,0:55:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我知道西蒙在撒谎 但其他人呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I knew that Simon was lying. But what about the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.44,0:55:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪彼得 那个保镖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Peter, the bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.88,0:55:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪如果都是假的 那他也骗我了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}If it wasn't real, then did he lie to me as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.16,0:55:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那个带孩子的女人是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Who is the woman with the kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.36,0:55:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那是西蒙的女儿吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Was that Simon's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.76,0:55:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我写信给美国运通卡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I write a message to Amex.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.84,0:55:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪能不能再给我提供一些信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Can you give me some more information?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.72,0:55:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他们告诉我谷歌希蒙·哈尤特 ‪我会找到答案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}They tell me to Google Shimon Hayut and that I will find some answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.28,0:55:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（谷歌搜索）
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.04,0:55:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪有一篇文章是芬兰语写的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}There's an article in Finnish.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.04,0:55:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（以色列“千万富翁”诈骗女性）
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.88,0:55:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以我点击了谷歌翻译\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So I go into Google Translate.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.28,0:55:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（以色列“千万富翁”诈骗女性）
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.48,0:55:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪以色列的千万富翁诈骗女性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Israeli multi-millionaire that cheated on women.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.52,0:56:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪搞什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.76,0:56:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（通过Tinder接触）
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.52,0:56:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（私人飞机）
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.48,0:56:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（奢华酒店）
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.56,0:56:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（这名男子诈骗了数万））
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.80,0:56:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪早在2015年时 ‪他就诈骗过三名芬兰女性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Back in 2015, he had been defrauding three Finnish women.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.44,0:56:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（）三名芬兰女性）
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.44,0:56:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪她们没有透露名字 她们受到保护\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}They don't give names. They are protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.56,0:56:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（持续危险）
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.16,0:56:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（逃到伦敦）
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.76,0:56:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他对一个女人说他是军火商\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He was saying that he was in the weapons industry to one of the women.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.48,0:56:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪对另一个女人说他是摩萨德特工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}To another woman, he said he was a Mossad agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.12,0:56:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（被法庭判刑）坐了三年牢））
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.16,0:56:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（严重欺诈）
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.16,0:56:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪太疯狂了 他进了监狱之后 ‪他对社会的危害更大了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}That's insane. He goes to prison. He becomes even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.40,0:56:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他们把一个带着新诈骗计划的犯人 ‪就这样放了出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}They let out a guy that has almost been, like, cooking up a new plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.88,0:56:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（需要更多钱）
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.56,0:56:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你知道他会继续不停地诈骗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}You knew he would just continue, continue, continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.56,0:56:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（她失去了工作）
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.48,0:56:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪有谁能阻止他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Who's gonna stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.72,0:56:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（威胁）
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.04,0:56:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（危险）
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.20,0:56:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（害怕）
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.36,0:56:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我必须阻止他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I had to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.04,0:56:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我要去找挪威最大的报社 VG\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I needed to go to the biggest newspaper in Norway, VG.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.32,0:57:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（谷歌搜索）
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.16,0:57:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我只是祈祷 他们会报导这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was just praying, you know, that they would take this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.20,0:57:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这真的是一个难以置信的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}This was really like an unbelievable story.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.76,0:57:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪一个人假装成是钻石大亨 ‪亿万富翁的儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}A guy who had pretended to be a son of a diamond billionaire.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.44,0:57:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪私人飞机 奢侈的生活方式 ‪听起来像童话故事或电影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Private jets, a luxury lifestyle. It, uh, sounds almost like a fairy tale or movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.80,0:57:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪作为记者 你首先会问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}First thing you ask as a journalist is
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.00,0:57:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪您可以与我们分享什么样的资料\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}what kind of documentation can you share with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.24,0:57:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪没有资料就无法出新闻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}You can't print it without documentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.20,0:57:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（你有任何文件或记录 ‪证明发生过的事吗）
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.84,0:57:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当然了 我有WhatsApp聊天记录\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Of course, I have WhatsApp.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.52,0:57:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（聊天记录）
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.76,0:57:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（聊天记录 西蒙）
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.28,0:57:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我之后想象到了陌生人阅读 ‪我的内心想法 恐惧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I then imagine strangers reading through my inner thoughts, my fears,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.84,0:57:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我对这个人的爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}my love for this guy, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.00,0:57:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这都非常私密 躺在床上的自拍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It's super private. It's selfies in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.60,0:58:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但证据是最重要的 我就发了过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}But the evidence came first, and I just sent it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.80,0:58:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪差不多有400页的聊天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It was almost 400 pages of text.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.72,0:58:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪还有视频\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}There's video.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.24,0:58:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪图片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.08,0:58:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪好 宝贝 我要起飞了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Okay, baby. I'm taking off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.16,0:58:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪语音消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Audio messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.72,0:58:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪太惊人了 就像在解剖二人的关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It's astounding. It's like looking into the anatomy of the relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.16,0:58:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们可以细化到每一分钟 ‪这个关系是如何发展的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We can follow how this developed minute by minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.12,0:58:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（第57页 共376页）
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.64,0:58:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他诈骗技术极其专业\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He's extremely professional in what he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.56,0:58:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪第一次约会是吸引她 ‪让她相信他很成功的好方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The first date was a good way to lure her to believe that he was really successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.48,0:58:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这是个情感骗局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}This is an emotional con.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.96,0:58:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（你和我）
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.24,0:58:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪他会承诺很多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He was promising so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.52,0:58:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪一起住在公寓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}an apartment together,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.68,0:58:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪一起度假\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}vacations,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.12,0:58:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪一起建立家庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}building a family together.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.20,0:58:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我把你看作未来的妻子 ‪我孩子的母亲）
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.72,0:58:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我想请你帮个忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I wanted to ask you a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.40,0:59:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪第一次要钱是在他们交往一个月后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The first request for money comes after they've been dating for over a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.32,0:59:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他用那一个月让她爱上他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And he has been using that month to make her fall in love with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.08,0:59:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪证明他很有钱 让她害怕他的敌人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}prove that he is really rich, and make her afraid of his enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.80,0:59:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪没理由相信西蒙没有偿还的能力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}There's no reason to believe that Simon is not able to pay her back,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.44,0:59:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为她已经见过他多有钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}because she has seen how wealthy he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.72,0:59:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙身边一直有很多人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon is surrounded by a lot of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.40,0:59:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪尤其是他的保镖和生意伙伴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}especially his bodyguard and his business partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.48,0:59:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们不知道是谁和西蒙合作 ‪这个阴谋进行到了哪一步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We don't know who is working with Simon and how far this conspiracy actually goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.52,0:59:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪塞西莉还给我们发了 ‪一篇芬兰语的文章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Cecilie was also sending us this Finnish article.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.28,0:59:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（以色列“百万富翁”诈骗女性）
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.80,0:59:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪希蒙·哈尤特和西蒙·列维耶夫 ‪是同一个人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Is Shimon Hayut and Simon Leviev the same guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.96,0:59:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们和当局取得了联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We all got in touch with the authorities
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.16,0:59:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪找到了三位受骗芬兰女性的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and found out the names of the three Finnish women.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.92,1:00:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我问塞西莉 ‪她认识这些受害者的名字吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I ask Cecilie, does she recognize the victims' names?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.28,1:00:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（原告）
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.16,1:00:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我在谷歌上搜索这些女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I Google these women.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.28,1:00:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我一个都不认识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I don't recognize anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.56,1:00:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后出现了一张很熟悉的脸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And then a face pops up that is very familiar.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.20,1:00:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪是跟我一起坐飞机的那个女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It's the same woman that was on the jet with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.08,1:00:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪和西蒙有孩子的那个女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The same woman that has a child with Simon.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.28,1:00:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你到底是怎么成为受害者的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}How on the fucking Earth were you a victim?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.32,1:00:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你在2016年的庭审中站了起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}You were standing at the trial back in 2016.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.44,1:00:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪把他关进了监狱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Putting him to jail,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.40,1:00:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪知道他曾经骗了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}knowing that he had lied to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.88,1:01:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪三年后 ‪你突然和西蒙一起坐私人飞机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and suddenly, three years later, you're sitting on a private jet with Simon.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.12,1:01:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪她在车里跟我说的那些话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The things that she told me in that car
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.00,1:01:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪让我真的相信他是个好人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}made me really believe that he was a great guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.48,1:01:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪她为什么没有警告我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Why didn't she warn me?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.96,1:01:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那太不寻常了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}That was extraordinary,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.04,1:01:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为这让我们不知道该相信谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and it made it hard because we didn't know who to trust.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.68,1:01:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但我们还得向警方证明希蒙·耶胡达 ‪哈尤特和西蒙·列维耶夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}But we still had to prove to the police that Shimon Yehuda Hayut and Simon Leviev
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.00,1:01:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪是同一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}was the same person.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.52,1:01:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（提供假的个人信息）
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.24,1:01:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪在起诉书中 ‪我们找到了他的出生日期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}In the indictment, we have his date of birth.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.12,1:01:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（出生日期）
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.12,1:01:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以当我们在谷歌里输入 ‪“希蒙·哈尤特”时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So when we typed in "Shimon Hayut" in Google,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.00,1:01:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪什么也没提供 ‪基本上没有有用的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}that didn't give us much, basically nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.48,1:02:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但西蒙·列维耶夫 ‪和希蒙·哈尤特有一个共同点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}But there's one thing that Simon Leviev and Shimon Hayut has in common.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.56,1:02:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他们都是以色列人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}They're both from Israel.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.24,1:02:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们需要懂希伯来语 ‪并了解以色列国的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We needed someone who knew Hebrew and knew the country of Israel.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.36,1:02:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（尤里·布劳 以色列记者）
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.48,1:02:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪所以我们联系了一位叫尤里的记者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So we contacted this journalist called Uri.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.84,1:02:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪尤里找到希蒙·哈尤特最近使用过的 ‪一个地址 我们得去趟以色列\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Uri finds out the last known address for Shimon Hayut. We need to go to Israel.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.16,1:02:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（以色列 特拉维夫）
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.48,1:02:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪驱车前往市郊 ‪我们看到更多狭窄的街道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We're driving towards the outskirts of the city, we see more narrow streets,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.44,1:02:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪更小的公寓楼 ‪很多极端正统的犹太人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}smaller apartment buildings, and a lot of ultra-Orthodox Jews.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.96,1:02:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这和他想在社交媒体上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}This was the total opposite
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.84,1:02:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪营造的自己的生活是截然相反的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}of how he wanted to present his life in social media.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.08,1:02:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪是这里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Is it here?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.60,1:03:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以让我们停在）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So let's park, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.00,1:03:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪-我要请你停在非常近的地方 ‪-好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}-I asked him to stay very near. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.04,1:03:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪以防我们需要脱身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}In case we need to escape.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.60,1:03:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪尤里 娜塔莉和我过去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Uri, Natalie, and I go out.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.16,1:03:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我的工作是作为摄影师 ‪记录发生的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}My job is to be the cameraman that documents everything that happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.72,1:03:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪就是这个名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}That's the name.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.76,1:03:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪就是这个名字 这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}That's the name. This one.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.76,1:03:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪上面写了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}What's it says?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.32,1:03:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这是给他的信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It's a letter for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.72,1:03:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪-给希蒙的 ‪-希蒙·哈尤特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}-For Shimon? -Shimon Hayut.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.40,1:03:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪是的 这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Yeah, this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.92,1:03:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以他可能现在住在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So he might actually be staying here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.80,1:03:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以这是政府\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So this is a letter from the authorities
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.80,1:03:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪要求欠债人员还钱的通知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}that ask money back from people when you owe money.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.76,1:03:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪哦 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.40,1:04:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.60,1:04:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你们是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.24,1:04:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们是记者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We're journalists.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.80,1:04:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们在找西蒙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We're looking for Simon.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.32,1:04:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.56,1:04:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪-你们不允许来这里 ‪-但是 妈妈 先进来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}-You are not allowed to be here. -But, Mom, come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.00,1:04:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以 你是西蒙的妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So, you're Simon's mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.24,1:04:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪-他在哪里 ‪-他在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}-Where is he? -Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.16,1:04:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你们在找他 我也在找他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}You're looking for him, I'm looking for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.48,1:04:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他在挪威骗了一个女人 ‪骗走了25万美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He's swindled a woman in Norway for a quarter of a million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.28,1:04:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我跟他完全没有联系 ‪我跟他一点关系都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I have absolutely no contact with him. I have nothing to do with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.76,1:04:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我从他18岁起就没跟他联系过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I've not had contact with him since he was 18 years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.68,1:04:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪-但他的注册地址在这里 ‪-他改了名字和地址\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}-But his registered address is here. -He changed his name and address.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.32,1:04:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他不再叫哈尤特了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He is not Hayut anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.24,1:04:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪-那他叫什么 ‪-列维耶夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}-So who is he? -Leviev.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.32,1:04:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.48,1:04:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪为了确认西蒙和希蒙是同一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}To confirm that Simon and Shimon was the same person,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.96,1:04:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们需要去见当地警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}we need to see the local police.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.12,1:04:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你熟悉这张脸吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Is this face familiar to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.08,1:04:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.04,1:05:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪在2017年 他更名为西蒙·列维耶夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}In 2017, he changed his name to Simon Leviev.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.56,1:05:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪在那之前 他被称为希蒙·哈尤特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Before that, he was known as Shimon Hayut.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.76,1:05:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪警方向我们证实 ‪西蒙·列维耶夫和希蒙·哈尤特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The police confirmed
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.56,1:05:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪就是在芬兰被定罪的那个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}that Simon Leviev and Shimon Hayut is the same guy convicted in Finland.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.32,1:05:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他用了很多名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He uses many names.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.68,1:05:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（迈克尔·比顿）
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.12,1:05:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（莫德凯·尼西姆·塔皮罗）
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.16,1:05:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他从十几岁开始就是个骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He has been a fraudster since his late teens.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.44,1:05:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（莫德凯·尼西姆·塔皮罗）
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.76,1:05:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你开始解开更多的谜题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}You start to piece together some more of the puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.16,1:05:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（以色列控告希蒙·耶胡达·哈尤特 ‪公诉书）
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.44,1:05:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪早在2011年时 ‪西蒙被指控盗窃老板的支票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Back in 2011, Simon was suspected of stealing a check from his employer.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.72,1:05:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他接着开始窃取并伪造其他支票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He moves on to other stolen checks and forged checks.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.92,1:05:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙本该在法庭上出席 ‪但他逃出国了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon was supposed to meet in court, but he fled the country.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.96,1:06:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪后来他离开了以色列 ‪他伪造了护照出国了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}But then he left Israel. He forged a passport and left the country.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.52,1:06:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以他被警方通缉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So he's wanted by the police?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.12,1:06:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.04,1:06:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪以色列当局要求找到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The Israeli authorities demand that he be found
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.44,1:06:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这样对他的审判才可以继续\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}so the trial against him can continue.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.08,1:06:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们正在尽力找到他 把他带回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And we're doing what we can to find him and bring him in.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.36,1:06:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们去了以色列之后 ‪得到了很多新的好消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We got a lot of new and really good information after the trip to Israel,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.28,1:06:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但是我们不知道他现在在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}but we don't know where he is right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.96,1:06:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我会随时通知你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Well, I will keep you posted.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.00,1:06:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪其他人都拿到钱了 ‪所以你也应该拿到钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Everybody else got their money, so you should too.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.32,1:06:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我看看发生了什么 ‪我晚点会打给银行 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I will see what's going on. I will call the bank.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.68,1:06:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪爱你 想你 再见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Love you. Miss you. Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.32,1:06:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他真诚地道歉 ‪然后说他要再多借一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He really apologizes and says that he needs to borrow a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.88,1:06:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我告诉他 “西蒙 你应该把借走的钱 ‪在一到两周后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I told him, "Simon, you were supposed to transfer back this money you borrowed
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.72,1:06:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪就还回来”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}a week or two after."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.20,1:06:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“你确定一切都没问题吗”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"Are you sure everything is gonna be okay?"
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.72,1:07:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他说 “是的 一切都没问题”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He's like, "Yeah, everything is gonna be okay."
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.32,1:07:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以我又转给他一万美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So I transfer him another $10,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.64,1:07:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我保证下周我会还给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I guarantee you I will make payment next week.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.48,1:07:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（谢谢你做的一切 圣诞快乐）
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.20,1:07:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（十万美元 付款记录.pdf）
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.60,1:07:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪第二周他给我发了一张 ‪十万美元的银行收据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The next week, he texts me a bank receipt for $100,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.48,1:07:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙很慷慨 他只欠我四万了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon is being very generous. He only owes me 40,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.52,1:07:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我的天啊 西蒙 我好惊讶）
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.56,1:07:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪哦 说真的 西蒙你真好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Oh, seriously, Simon, that is so nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.24,1:07:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪谢谢 太谢谢你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Thank you. Thank you. Thank you. Thank you so, so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.12,1:07:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪亲亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Kisses.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.48,1:07:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪在最艰难的时刻 你一直支持我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Through the most difficult moments, you have been there for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.24,1:07:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以这也是为什么 ‪我想发自内心地感谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So that's why I wanted to thank you from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.32,1:07:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后那笔钱就一直没到账\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And then the money just don't arrive.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.44,1:07:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪不幸地是 银行希望我本人到场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Unfortunately, the bank want me there physically
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.20,1:07:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪和我的律师一起签署一些文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}with my lawyer to sign some few other papers.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.36,1:08:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我得飞过去 把事情处理好 ‪我想请你帮个忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I need to fly and I need to fix it up. I want to ask you a favor.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.00,1:08:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以我用美国运通卡 ‪付了这些航班的费用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So I pay for these flights on my American Express card.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.84,1:08:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪钱已经从我们的银行账户划走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The money has left our bank account
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.36,1:08:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以你不用担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}so you have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.36,1:08:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他又请求我帮他付了另一张机票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He asked me to help him with another flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.44,1:08:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后又是一张接一张的机票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And then another flight, and then another flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.76,1:08:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以随着时间过去了很久 ‪钱就是不到账\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So with time just passing, money doesn't come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.52,1:08:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我刚才就在银行 ‪他们找不到任何转账记录
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.52,1:08:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪而且我真的需要付清账单 ‪我真的好害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was just at the bank and they can't find any transfer. And that I need to pay my bills. I'm really freaking out.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.16,1:08:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我很慌张 我现在惹了很多很多麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm panicking. Like, I got myself in so, so much trouble right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.20,1:08:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他们冻结了我的账户\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}They put a stop on my account.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.72,1:08:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当然我可以给你一只我的手表\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Of course I can give you one of my watches.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.72,1:08:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪我有一只价值超过十万的手表\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I have a watch worth over 100K.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.60,1:08:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以他告诉我他会给我 ‪订张机票去他那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So he tells me he will book me a flight to wherever he is
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.40,1:08:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他会在几天之内找出那只手表\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}within a couple of days to collect the watch.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.00,1:09:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们得到很多新信息 ‪但我们还没找到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We have a lot of new information, but we still haven't found him.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.76,1:09:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以我们需要做的 ‪是回到塞西莉给我们的记录里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So what we have to do is go back into the documentation we got from Cecilie.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.04,1:09:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（美国运通白金卡 账户明细表）
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.92,1:09:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪塞西莉用她的美国运通卡 ‪转账了很多次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Cecilie gave us a lot of transactions done with her Amex card.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.76,1:09:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪在这些转账中 我们看到了多张机票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}In these transactions, we see flight tickets.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.48,1:09:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪上面还有名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}There are also names.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.88,1:09:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那位生意伙伴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The business partner.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.84,1:09:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪保镖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.64,1:09:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但我们也可以找到不同女性的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}But we could also find names of different women.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.52,1:09:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以其中一个名字是佩妮拉·舍霍姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So one of the names is Pernilla Sjoholm.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.40,1:09:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（佩妮拉·舍霍姆的搜索结果）
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.08,1:10:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以我在脸书上找到佩妮拉 ‪给她发了一条私信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So I find Pernilla on Facebook and write a message to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.56,1:10:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（你好 我是一名记者）
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.60,1:10:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（厄伦德·阿恩森 ‪给你发送了一条信息）
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.04,1:10:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（打开）
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.96,1:10:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（你好 我是一名记者）
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.04,1:10:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（在挪威的VG报纸上）
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.72,1:10:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（西蒙·列维耶夫）
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.52,1:10:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（骗）
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.96,1:10:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（大数额的）
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.32,1:10:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（钱）
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.68,1:10:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（这是真的吗）
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.68,1:10:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我）慌了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I... panic.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.24,1:10:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我感觉都要昏过去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I thought I was gonna pass out.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.20,1:10:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我把消息直接发给西蒙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I forward the message straight over to Simon.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.36,1:10:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我不会让）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I would not...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.28,1:10:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他说我不应该担心 ‪这是他的敌人在套取情报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He says I shouldn't worry, that this is his enemies trying to get information.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.76,1:10:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他真的努力让我冷静下来 ‪在挂断电话后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He really tries to calm me down and even just, like, after hanging up the phone,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.52,1:10:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我开始意识到 这不可能是编造的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm starting to realize, like, this can't be made up.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.04,1:10:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（厄伦德·阿恩森）
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.32,1:10:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我的手机响了 是厄伦德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}My phone rings. It is Erlend.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.56,1:11:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以我问她 “我能来斯德哥尔摩 ‪跟你谈谈你的故事吗”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So I asked her, "Can I come to Stockholm to meet you to talk through your story?"
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.16,1:11:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我上了飞机 我们第二天要见面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I get on a plane. We were meeting up the next day.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.48,1:11:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（瑞典 斯德哥尔摩）
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.84,1:11:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他把一切都告诉我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He tells me everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.88,1:11:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我很生气 西蒙为什么要这样对我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I am furious. Why would Simon do this to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.08,1:11:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他是我真正关心的朋友 我爱的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}This was a friend who I really cared about, who I loved.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.28,1:11:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他创造了一个我会喜欢的形象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He really created this person that I would like,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.04,1:11:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪一个能成为我好朋友的形象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}someone who would be a really good friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.12,1:11:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以 如果他不只是 ‪通过浪漫关系来实施骗术\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So, if it's not only through romantic relationships that he's pursuing scams,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.44,1:11:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪还会有哪些花招呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}what else could there be?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.36,1:11:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我告诉厄伦德所有旅行的经历 ‪和他花的那么多钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I tell Erlend about all the travels and the amount of money he has been spending,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.24,1:11:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪还有我遇见的所有其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and all the other people that I have met.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.44,1:11:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当他告诉我这个挪威女孩时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}When he tells me about this Norwegian girl,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.88,1:12:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我开始意识到她损失的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm starting to realize that the amount of money she has lost
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.68,1:12:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪根本不够覆盖他一直以来的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}doesn't add up to the lifestyle that he's been living,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.20,1:12:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为已经花出去的钱 数额巨大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}because there is an extreme amount of money that has been spent.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.68,1:12:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这肯定只是冰山一角\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}This must just be the tip of the iceberg.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.12,1:12:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪看了佩妮拉的银行账户后 ‪我发现这可能是庞氏骗局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}After looking at Pernilla's bank accounts, I realize this may be a Ponzi scheme.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.56,1:12:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他把塞西莉的钱用在了佩妮拉身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He uses Cecilie's money on Pernilla,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.68,1:12:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他会把佩妮拉的钱用在别人身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and he uses Pernilla's money on somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.48,1:12:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪信用卡上从来不是他的名字 ‪所以他有合法的理由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It's never his name on the credit card, so he has plausible excuse.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.96,1:12:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他总能说 “我只是借钱而已”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He can always say, "I was just borrowing the money."
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.72,1:12:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这几乎是完美的骗局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It's almost like the perfect scam.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.64,1:12:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当然 用一个女人的信用卡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Of course, by using one woman's credit card
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.80,1:12:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪去给第二个女人买机票 ‪然后请第三个人吃晚餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}to buy plane tickets to a second woman and to buy a dinner to a third,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.16,1:13:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他经常旅行 ‪而且从不在一个地方呆太久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}he was able to travel a lot, and he never stayed long in one place.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.00,1:13:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这使得预算较低的当地警方很难去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}That made it very hard for local police authorities with low budgets
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.04,1:13:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪追查这样一个男人 ‪在他们的世界里 这就是个小骗局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}to go after a man that, in their world, was like a small scam.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.16,1:13:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪喂 我们点了整个菜单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Hey, we order all the menu.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.32,1:13:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我问佩妮拉 ‪“你能告诉我他在哪儿吗”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I ask Pernilla, "Can you tell me where he is?"
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.72,1:13:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我不仅知道他在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I don't just only know where he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.48,1:13:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我还订了机票明天要去见他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I am booked on a flight to go and see him tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.24,1:13:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他在慕尼黑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He's in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.92,1:13:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪再过十小时 我们就要去慕尼黑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}In less than 10 hours, we need to be in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.60,1:13:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（德国 慕尼黑）
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.36,1:13:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们在慕尼黑的目标是拍摄到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Our goal in Munich was to film him
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.24,1:13:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪向警方证明 他是可以被追查到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}to prove to the police that he was possible to find.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.56,1:13:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你真的要很专注\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}You're really focused.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.68,1:13:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你知道你只有这一次机会 ‪拍到想要的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}You know you have this one chance to get what you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.72,1:14:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪而且你也要对佩妮拉负责\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Also you have responsibility for Pernilla.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.88,1:14:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙绝对不能发现他们来了 ‪是我带他们来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon can absolutely not find out that they are there or that I have done this,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.60,1:14:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为我不知道如果他发现了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}because I don't know if it's dangerous for me
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.04,1:14:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我背着他这样做 ‪会不会对我造成危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}if he does find out that I'm doing this behind his back.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.04,1:14:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我要去破坏他的美好生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm going in there trying to sabotage his fabulous life.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.84,1:14:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪计划是要保持一个安全的距离\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The plan is to keep a safe distance,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.80,1:14:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪要想做到这点 娜塔莉会在手机上 ‪追踪佩妮拉的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and to do that, Natalie is tracking Pernilla's whereabouts on the iPhone.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.72,1:14:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪以防西蒙查看佩妮拉的手机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}In case Simon should look at Pernilla's phone,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.04,1:14:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪佩妮拉用另一个名字给我备注\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Pernilla saves my number as a different name.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.76,1:14:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这让佩妮拉可以和我保持联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}That makes it possible for Pernilla to have constant contact with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.68,1:14:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪她发信息说她刚降落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}She writes that she's just landed.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.92,1:14:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们在机场外面安排了摄影师 ‪可能会拍到照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We have a photographer outside the airport who may be able to get pictures.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.64,1:14:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪她发消息说 “我朋友来接我”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}She writes, "My friend is picking me up."
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.20,1:14:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那一定是西蒙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}That must be Simon.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.28,1:15:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我刚刚收到了摄影师的照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I've now received a picture from the photographer.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.44,1:15:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪哇 他真在慕尼黑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Wow, he's in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.44,1:15:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我的心在狂跳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}My heart is pounding.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.40,1:15:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这是我第一次见到他的商业伙伴 ‪阿维谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}This is the first time I meet his business partner, Avishay,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.96,1:15:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他跟我讲过很多他的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}that he had told me so much about.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.44,1:15:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我开始变得非常疑神疑鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm starting to become very, very paranoid
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.88,1:15:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为我不知道跟我坐一辆车的人是谁 ‪他们到底是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}because who am I in the car with? Who are they really?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.00,1:15:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我看着他 我知道真相 ‪知道他所做的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm looking at him, and I know the truth, like everything that he has done.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.64,1:15:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那种以前把他当成朋友的感觉没有了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}These former feelings that I had that this was my friend just got erased.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.64,1:15:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我觉得我这辈子从来没有恨过一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I don't think I ever hated a person my entire life
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.24,1:15:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪直到我坐在车里 看着他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}until that second when I was sitting in that car
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.52,1:15:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那一刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and just looking at him.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.92,1:15:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（我们准备好了 ‪告诉我们你们准备去哪儿）
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.88,1:15:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪佩妮拉给我发短信说 ‪他们要去文华东方酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Pernilla texted me that they were going to Mandarin Oriental Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.72,1:16:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那是一家里面有餐厅的高级酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}That's a fancy hotel with a restaurant inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.24,1:16:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.92,1:16:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我在那里最重要的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The most important job I had in there
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.16,1:16:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪就是在他们离开餐厅时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}was to text Kristoffer and the still photographer
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.68,1:16:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪给克里斯托弗和固定摄影师发短信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}whenever they were leaving the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.96,1:16:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪对面有个停车场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Opposite, there's a parking garage.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.36,1:16:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪就在墙的缝隙后面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Just behind gaps in the wall,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.68,1:16:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们可以架好镜头 ‪等西蒙出来的时候抓拍他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}we can place our lenses to capture Simon as he walks out.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.24,1:16:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪大家都认识他“欢迎回来 ‪列维耶夫先生”这让我开始联想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Everyone knew about him. "Welcome back, Mr. Leviev." And that gets me going.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.40,1:16:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你在慕尼黑做什么 ‪这里有多少受害者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}What have you been doing in Munich? How many victims are here?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.84,1:16:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他告诉我 他对那笔钱很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He tells me he's sorry about the situation with the money
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.28,1:16:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他只能给我这个手表\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and he gives me the watch.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.68,1:16:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他点了菜单上的全部菜品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He orders everything on the menu,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.84,1:16:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们吃晚餐的时候 ‪我坐在那里感觉很难受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and I feel so bad even sitting there when we're having this dinner,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.56,1:16:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为我脑子里唯一的想法就是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}'cause the only thing that goes in my head is,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.12,1:16:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“谁在付这顿晚餐”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"Who's paying for this dinner?"
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.36,1:16:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们就在一直等娜塔莉发消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We're just waiting and waiting for a text from Natalie.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.64,1:16:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（他们走的时候 我告诉你）
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.04,1:17:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我们到街对面了 一切就绪）
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.64,1:17:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（他们现在离开了）
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.00,1:17:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙看着我们的方向 我们躲了起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon looks in our direction, and we hide.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.76,1:17:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙开始说希伯来语 ‪然后对阿维谢非常生气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon starts speaking in Hebrew and getting very upset to Avishay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.88,1:17:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我在想 “怎么回事”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And I'm like, "What's going on?"
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.56,1:17:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他们像在说 “那边有个摄像头”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And they were like, "There's a camera guy over there."
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.48,1:17:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后他开始大叫 “上车”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And he started screaming, like, "Get into the car!"
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.88,1:17:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪在慕尼黑市区开得很快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Driving around so fast through Munich.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.36,1:17:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我不知道他们在说什么 ‪他们知道是我安排的摄影师吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I don't know what they're saying. Do they know that I have set them up to do this?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.16,1:17:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他们要把我怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}What are they really gonna do with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.16,1:18:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你想想“佩妮拉 ‪你要展现出你一辈子最大的演技\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Just think, like, "Pernilla, you play your biggest act you have ever done
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.48,1:18:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为否则你永远回不了家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}your entire life, because otherwise you are never coming home."
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.12,1:18:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我在努力扭曲事实 反将一军\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm trying to twist everything around.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.08,1:18:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我对他大喊 “这是你的敌人吗 ‪他们现在是在追我吗 西蒙”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm screaming at him, like, "Is this your enemies? Are they after me now, Simon?"
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.36,1:18:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他想让局面平静下来 ‪说 “不 他们追的不是你 是我”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He's trying to calm down the situation, like, "No, it's me they're after."
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.48,1:18:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我跟他说 “让我下车”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm telling him, "Just drop me off."
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.00,1:18:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我这辈子从来没那么快地打开车门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I never opened a car door as fast in my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.16,1:18:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们非常担心佩妮拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We were very concerned about Pernilla.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.76,1:18:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们发现我们在那里没能拍到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We realized we wouldn't be able to confront him there.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.08,1:18:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们需要回到奥斯陆 ‪思考下一步如何行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We need to go back to Oslo and work out our next step.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.76,1:19:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我拿着手表去了当铺 他们说是假的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I take the watch to a pawn shop, and they tell me it is fake.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.48,1:19:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当然了 因为他的事没一件是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Of course it is, because nothing about him is real.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.32,1:19:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我真的很想跟他面对面对峙 ‪至少告诉我真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I really want to confront him and at least tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.40,1:19:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这就是你想要从大家那里得到的 ‪至少告诉我真相 是怎样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}That's what you want from all people. Just tell me the truth, how it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.68,1:19:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪佩妮拉很想跟他谈谈 ‪我们正在拍摄那通电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Pernilla really wants to talk to him, and we are filming that call.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.28,1:19:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.88,1:19:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪嗨 你好吗 早上好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Hey, what's up? Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.28,1:19:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪早上好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.20,1:19:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪下午好 抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Good afternoon. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.40,1:19:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪没关系 你在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It's okay. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.04,1:19:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我没事 你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm all right, and you?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.04,1:19:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我不太好 西蒙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm not so good, Simon.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.08,1:19:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.52,1:19:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你能告诉我实话吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Can you just tell me the truth?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.20,1:19:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我说的就是实话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I told you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.24,1:19:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪不对 你没有告诉我实话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}No, you haven't told me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.36,1:19:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你能告诉我全部真相吗 ‪我至少值得知道全部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Can you give me the entire truth? At least I deserve that.
