Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.60,1:20:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你这辈子都要为此付出代价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}you will pay for this for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.00,1:20:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我确实要余生都付出代价 ‪你夺走了我拥有的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I am paying for the rest of my life. You took everything I have.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.40,1:20:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这是你的错 如果你想指控我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}This is your mistake. If you want to make some claims against me,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.60,1:20:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪把你掌握的对我不利的证据给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}give me the evidence you have against me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.44,1:20:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪以色列警方已经确认了你的照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The Israeli police have confirmed you with your picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.04,1:20:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪没有人确认任何事 这都不是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Nobody has confirmed anything. That's not true.
