Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.20,1:21:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我确实给了他们钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I did give them money.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.52,1:21:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙 你不能一直这样下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon, you can't keep doing this.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.84,1:21:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这样太疯狂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Like, it's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.24,1:21:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪亲爱的 你做这一切是为了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Honey, what have you done this all for?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.64,1:21:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你会付出代价的 ‪而且我保证代价会比钱更多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}There will be a price, and I promise it'll be bigger than money.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.60,1:21:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你说的代价是指什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}What do you mean, the price?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.72,1:21:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你出卖了我 你要为此付出代价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}You double-cross me, you're gonna pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.08,1:21:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我真的很害怕 因为我做了什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I really got scared, because what have I done?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.52,1:21:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们唯一能做的就是把新闻版面 ‪在VG报纸上做大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The only thing that we can do is to make the VG piece as big as possible
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.36,1:21:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪让他的脸公之于众\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}to get his face out there,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.88,1:21:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为如果人们知道他是谁 ‪认出他的长相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}because if people would know who he is and recognize his face,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.88,1:21:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他就不能再为非作歹了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}he can't do this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.52,1:21:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪站出来 讲述出这样一个故事 ‪需要很大的勇气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Coming forward with a story like this takes a lot of courage.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.76,1:21:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我感到非常焦虑 ‪VG是挪威最出名的报纸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was feeling anxious, you know. VG is the biggest newspaper in Norway.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.40,1:21:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我的脸会出现在封面上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Like, my face would be on the front cover.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.96,1:22:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪会有一个大型的网络特辑来讲述\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}There would be this big online special.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.84,1:22:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我知道人们会评判我 ‪我准备好了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I know that people were gonna judge me. Am I ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.16,1:22:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（评论）
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.20,1:22:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你的整个人生都不会再和以前一样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Your entire life is never gonna be the same again.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.32,1:22:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（女人太容易上当受骗了 ‪她真是个白痴）
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.16,1:22:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（哈哈 废物）
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.88,1:22:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（只看到了他的钱）
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.08,1:22:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪一切就像野火一样 一发不可收拾 ‪这感觉就是一场噩梦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Everything just, like, went wildfire. It felt like a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.32,1:22:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（加载更多评论）
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.32,1:22:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪社交媒体是残酷的 ‪他们会把你生吞活剥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Social media is brutal, you know. They'll eat you alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.24,1:22:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪人们都说你是个拜金女 ‪或者说"她活该"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}People are saying what a gold digger you are or, "She deserved this."
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.24,1:22:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪一个拜金女是不会往外花一分钱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}A gold digger would never give out a penny.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.44,1:22:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我一直不明白 你怎么能责怪受害者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I never understood this, how you can blame a victim.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.52,1:22:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（太天真了）
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.36,1:22:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我所做的只是想帮助别人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}All I did was just trying to help people.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.40,1:22:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我不想再让任何人受到伤害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I didn't want anyone else to get hurt.
