Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.48,1:22:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（贪婪）
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.72,1:22:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（她怎么会是贪婪呢）
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.80,1:22:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但我还是很高兴能看到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}But it was kind of nice to just see
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.64,1:23:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪也试着关注人们写的积极评论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and try to focus on the positive things that people were writing.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.28,1:23:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（别怪受害者）
