Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.20,1:23:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（难以置信的悲伤故事）
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.76,1:23:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（希望她一切顺利）
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.20,1:23:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我能看到分享的数量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I could see the amount of shares.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.48,1:23:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪一条又一条的评论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Comment after comment after comment.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.60,1:23:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“看看这个故事” “简直太疯狂了”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"Look at this story," you know. "It's just insane."
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.88,1:23:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们坐在那里看着数字不断上升\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We were sitting there watching the numbers go up and up.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.52,1:23:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪每个人都想读读“Tinder 诈骗王” ‪这故事迅速传播开来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Everybody wanted to read The Tinder Swindler. It was going viral.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.84,1:23:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这就是我想要的 他的脸在报道中 ‪他的名字也赫然其中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}This is what I wanted. His face is there. His name is there.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.92,1:23:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪不管他遇到谁 当他说 ‪“嗨 我叫西蒙·列维耶夫”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}No matter who he meets and he says, "Hi. My name is Simon Leviev,"
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.88,1:23:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那一刻大家谷歌他的时候 ‪故事就会出现于眼前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}the moment they Google him now, it will be there.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.84,1:23:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我遇见了佩妮拉 ‪很快 我们之间产生了共鸣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I met Pernilla. Immediately, we had a bond.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.72,1:23:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这是唯一一个真正理解 ‪我所经历之事的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}This is the only person who really understands what I am going through.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.36,1:23:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们希望保持这种势头 ‪我们整合了各势力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We wanted to keep the momentum up. We joined forces.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.32,1:24:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们都有一个目标 ‪那就是要让这篇文章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Both of us had a goal that this needed to come out
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.52,1:24:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪在尽可能多的国家的报纸上发表\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}in as many newspapers in as many countries as possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.44,1:24:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪-你好 ‪-嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}-Hello. -Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.32,1:24:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪首先我想道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}First of all, I wanted to apologize
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.80,1:24:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪并想让你们知道 ‪并不是所有的以色列男人都是骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and let you know that not all Israeli men are such crooks.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.00,1:24:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪参加美国 英国 荷兰还有德国的 ‪脱口秀和新闻机构\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Talk shows and news agencies in the US, UK, Netherlands, Germany as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.20,1:24:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们需要更多的曝光 ‪更多的国家进行自己的调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We needed more exposure and more countries to make their own investigations.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.96,1:24:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪比如“他在我们国家做了什么 ‪我们国家是否存在受害者”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Like, "What did he do in our country? Do we have any victims here?"
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.00,1:24:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但另一个目的则是让警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}But another thing was to actually get the police
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.44,1:24:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪感受到来自媒体和公众的压力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}to feel the pressure from the media, the pressure from the public,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.52,1:24:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪并对此采取行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and do something about this.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.60,1:24:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪反响非常热烈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The response was really overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.80,1:24:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪世界各地的受害者都联系了我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We were contacted by victims all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.08,1:24:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我是2015年在Tinder上认识他的 ‪我们在哥本哈根见面）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I met him on Tinder in 2015. We met up Copenhagen...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.56,1:24:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们约会了大约六个月 ‪他见了我的家人和朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We dated for around six months. He met my family and friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.64,1:25:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他在纽约和我们住在一起 ‪他说他叫希蒙·耶胡达·哈尤特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He stayed with us in New York. He said his name was Shimon Yehuda Hayut.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.28,1:25:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪-他的名字叫莫德凯·塔皮罗 ‪-他的名字叫西蒙·列维耶夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}- His name was Mordechay Tapiro. - His name was Simon Leviev.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.68,1:25:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我和妻子雇西蒙照顾我们五岁的儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}My wife and I hired Simon to babysit our five-year-old son.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.52,1:25:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当时他20岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He was 20 years old at the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.28,1:25:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们知道他的父亲是位犹太教教士 ‪他来自一个非常）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We knew that his father was a rabbi and he came from a very...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.52,1:25:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他告诉我他是以色列一家航空公司的 ‪继承人 他雇我当他的私人助理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He told me he was heir to an Israeli airline. He employed me as his PA.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.80,1:25:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他雇我当他的私人司机 ‪他还租了很多豪车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He hired me as his personal chauffeur. And he hired a lot of expensive cars.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.12,1:25:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪30万美元的账单 他一直没付钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He never paid the bill. $300,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.80,1:25:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他告诉我 ‪他是摩萨德特工的卧底飞行员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He told me that he was a Mossad agent working undercover as a pilot.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.36,1:25:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他花了近两万美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He spent nearly $20,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.52,1:25:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪仅仅三天 他就用我们的运通卡 ‪花了四万两千美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}In just three days, he spent $42,000 on our Amex card.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.44,1:25:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们有三张支票是伪造的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Three of our checks had been forged.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.80,1:25:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪总额近五万美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Nearly $50,000 in total.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.76,1:25:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（信用卡诈骗）
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.04,1:25:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪六年过去了 我还是没有释怀 ‪我很害怕他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm still not over it, six years later. I'm scared of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.20,1:26:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们有全部这些信息 ‪但他却相安无事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We got all this information, but nothing happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.28,1:26:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他仍逍遥法外 他仍是一个自由人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He was still on the run, he was still a free man,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.40,1:26:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪尽管我们知道他已经被别人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}even though we knew that he was reported to the police
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.00,1:26:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪向至少七个国家的警方报案了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}in at least seven different countries.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.52,1:26:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（捷克共和国 布拉格）
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.44,1:26:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我当时是在布拉格机场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was at the airport in Prague.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.08,1:26:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我是去看我的男朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I had been visiting my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.20,1:26:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪在等飞机起飞的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}While I was waiting for my plane to leave,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.40,1:26:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪我刷着Instagram ‪看到了我男朋友的照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was scrolling through Instagram, and I saw the picture of my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.44,1:26:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我点了进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I clicked on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.48,1:26:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪Tinder 诈骗王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"The Tinder Swindler"?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.12,1:26:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这是什么情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}What the fuck is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.36,1:26:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（引诱）
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.04,1:26:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我完全震惊了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was completely in shock.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.32,1:26:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我把文章发给西蒙 ‪他就开始给我打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I sent the article to Simon, and he started calling me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.16,1:26:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们就要起飞了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We were about to take off,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.20,1:26:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以我下载了这篇文章 ‪并把手机调到了飞行模式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}so I downloaded the article and put my phone on airplane mode.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.72,1:27:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我看到这个叫塞西莉的女孩 ‪在Tinder上认识了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I saw that this girl Cecilie met him on Tinder.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.12,1:27:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我也是在Tinder上认识的他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I also met him on Tinder.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.36,1:27:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪第一次约会 ‪他也带我去了一家五星级酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He also took me to a five-star hotel on the first date.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.88,1:27:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我当时已经和西蒙约会了14个月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was already dating Simon for 14 months.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.36,1:27:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以我们的关系很认真\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So we were in a serious relationship.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.56,1:27:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我非常爱他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I loved him very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.48,1:27:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他很体贴 会记住每一件小事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He was very thoughtful. He would remember every little thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.92,1:27:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我全身心地投入 和他交往\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I shared my whole heart with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.88,1:27:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们都开始讨论一起安定下来 ‪组建一个家庭了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We started talking about settling down together, starting a family.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.52,1:27:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我真的感觉我们是天生的一对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I really felt we were meant for each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.96,1:28:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（2018年1月 塞西莉遇到了一个 ‪名叫西蒙·列维耶夫的人）
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.60,1:28:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我浏览了那篇文章 ‪看到了附带的那些视频\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was scrolling through the article. I saw these videos coming up.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.88,1:28:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪塞西莉 我亲爱的 我爱你 我很想你 ‪我等不及要见你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Cecilie, my love, I love you. I miss you. I can't wait to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.20,1:28:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他给我发了同样的视频\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He sent me the same video.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.40,1:28:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪艾琳 亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Ayleen, darling,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.04,1:28:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我很想你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I miss you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.08,1:28:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Peter.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.44,1:28:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我浏览了一下我的WhatsApp聊天记录 ‪然后开始比较\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I went through my WhatsApp history, and I started to compare.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.00,1:28:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他对她说的话和对我说的一模一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He was sending exactly the same words to her as he did to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.36,1:28:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“早上好 亲爱的 你好吗 我爱你 ‪我很想你”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"Good morning, love. How are you? I love you. I miss you."
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.40,1:28:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“我想跟你生孩子”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"I wanna have babies with you."
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.88,1:28:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他带塞西莉去了阿姆斯特丹 ‪那是我的家乡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He took Cecilie to Amsterdam, my hometown.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.40,1:28:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪就在和我们交往的相同阶段\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Exactly the same period as we were dating,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.44,1:28:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪她当时在找房子 ‪准备和他一起在伦敦生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}she was looking for houses to start living with him in London.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.72,1:28:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我当时也在阿姆斯特丹找房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was also looking for houses in Amsterdam.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.76,1:28:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（惊喜 到了奥斯陆）
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.68,1:29:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪就在同一天 他飞往奥斯陆出差\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The same day, he was flying to Oslo for a business trip,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.60,1:29:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他当时只是要去见她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}he was just going out to see her.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.12,1:29:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他给我发短信说 “我累死了” ‪是的 当然了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He texted me, "I'm tired as fuck." Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.28,1:29:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他整晚都在塞西莉身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He was with Cecilie all night.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.44,1:29:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（听说事情进展不顺利 我很遗憾）
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.44,1:29:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他告诉我在慕尼黑的交易出了问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He told me that this business deal in Munich went wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.32,1:29:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但他当时是在见佩妮拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}But he was meeting Pernilla.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.16,1:29:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪彼得倒下了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Peter is down!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.08,1:29:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他给我发了一模一样的照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He sent exactly the same pictures to me,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.52,1:29:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪告诉我他的敌人把彼得打倒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}telling me that his enemies had beaten Peter up.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.88,1:29:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我真的很担心）
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.84,1:29:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当我收到那些照片时 我感到很害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}When I got those pictures, I was terrified.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.68,1:29:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（但这真的很可怕）
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.88,1:29:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这让我变得多疑 不停地四处张望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It made me paranoid, constantly looking over my shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.64,1:29:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪几年前 我被两个家伙跟踪 ‪他们揍了我一顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}A few years ago, I was followed by two guys and they beat me up.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.52,1:29:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我跟西蒙说了这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I told Simon about this.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.72,1:30:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当西蒙说我被跟踪时 ‪那段时间我一直都很焦虑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}When Simon said I was being followed, I was full of anxiety all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.48,1:30:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我睡不着觉 压力很大）
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.76,1:30:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪我看到他是个逃犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm reading that he is a fugitive.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.20,1:30:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（列维耶夫在以色列被通缉）
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.84,1:30:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪一个已被定罪的罪犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}A convicted criminal.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.92,1:30:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（被定罪）
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.40,1:30:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（诈骗了数百万）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He swindled women for millions.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.96,1:30:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我的心都快停止跳动了 ‪因为我也借钱给了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}My heart almost stopped beating, because I also lent him money.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.52,1:30:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（其他被他骗过的女人 ‪都在为他的奢侈买单）
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.76,1:30:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪一开始数额很小\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It started off small.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.84,1:30:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他的敌人在追踪他的手机 ‪所以他让我弄些电话卡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}His enemies were tracking his phones, so he asked me to get some SIM cards.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.88,1:30:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以我付清了那些账单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So I was paying off those bills.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.12,1:30:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但数额变得越来越多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}But it became more and more and more.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.16,1:30:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我给了他14万美元 一笔巨款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I gave him $140,000. So much money.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.12,1:30:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪名牌服装 其他女人的机票 ‪高档的晚宴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Designer clothes, flight tickets for other women. Fancy dinners.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.32,1:31:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪现在我明白了 ‪他把我的钱都挥霍在了谎言上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Now I see, my money he spent on basically bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.76,1:31:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我百感交集\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I had so many emotions.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.44,1:31:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪关于被骗的部分 还有钱的部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The cheating part, the money part.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.88,1:31:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪坐上一次小小的航班 ‪我就失去了一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}On one small flight, I lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.52,1:31:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我不想让飞机着陆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I didn't want the plane to land,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.64,1:31:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为我需要面对现实 ‪而现实是可怕的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}because I needed to face reality, and that reality was terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.04,1:31:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我一到阿姆斯特丹 ‪我就知道他会打电话给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The moment I land in Amsterdam, I knew he would call me.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.64,1:31:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪）愉快的飞行 谢谢您搭乘我们的航班 ‪祝您有一个愉快的夜晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}...an enjoyable flight. Thank you for flying with us, and have a pleasant evening.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.12,1:31:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（西蒙 未接语音通话）
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.80,1:31:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我是说 我不知道这是哪儿来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I mean, I don't know where this shit came from.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.32,1:32:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他说这篇文章是假的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He says the article was fake.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.92,1:32:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪塞西莉和佩妮拉 ‪可能是被他的敌人收买\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Cecilie and Pernilla would have been paid by his enemies
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.16,1:32:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪来写这篇文章的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}to create this article.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.68,1:32:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我知道我被骗了 我知道他是个骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I knew I was defrauded. I knew that he was fake.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.60,1:32:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪听着 我爱你 我在乎你）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}-I love you. I care about you--
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.64,1:32:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（紧急呼叫）
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.68,1:32:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我跟警察报了案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I talked to the police.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.40,1:32:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪他们说他们需要时间来立案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}They said they needed time to build this case,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.32,1:32:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪但时间正是我没有的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}but it was something I didn't have,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.84,1:32:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪因为我知道西蒙是个逃犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}because I knew that Simon was a fugitive.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.16,1:32:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪一旦他能离开 他就会立马逃走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The moment he was able to get away, he would.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.44,1:32:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我不想让他逃走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I didn't want him to get away with this.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.48,1:32:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我想和文章里的人谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I wanted to talk to someone who was in the article.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.08,1:32:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（佩妮拉）
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.40,1:32:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我在Instagram上找到了佩妮拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I found Pernilla on Instagram.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.32,1:32:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我收到一个名叫艾琳 ‪荷兰女孩的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So I get a message from this Dutch girl, Ayleen,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.68,1:33:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪她说她是西蒙的女朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}saying that she's the girlfriend of Simon,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.36,1:33:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪她看到了这片文章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and she has seen the story
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.32,1:33:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪并说她感觉自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and says that it feels like
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.68,1:33:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪现在正处于一部恐怖电影之中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}she is in the middle of a horror movie right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.36,1:33:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.28,1:33:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪艾琳说她会帮我们抓住他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Ayleen says she's going to help us catch him,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.48,1:33:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但她需要先做一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}but there's something she needs to do first.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.08,1:33:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我很抱歉）
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.36,1:33:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我要拿回我的钱 但要怎么做 ‪我得想个计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I needed to get my money back. But how? I had to come up with a plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.16,1:33:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我的脸都出现在新闻上了 ‪到处都是）
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.08,1:33:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪突然我发现自己的处境很有优势\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Suddenly I realized I was in a quite powerful position.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.84,1:33:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（西蒙·列维耶夫）
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.32,1:33:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他再也没办法骗到Tinder上任何女性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He wasn't able to get any women on Tinder anymore
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.88,1:33:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为在谷歌上全是他的脸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}because his face was all over Google.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.68,1:33:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以他躲在布拉格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So he was hiding in Prague
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.32,1:33:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪除了我 他绝对没有别的地方可去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and he had absolutely nowhere else to go besides me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.64,1:33:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他总是告诉我 要让你的朋友在身边 ‪敌人更要在身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He always told me keep your friends close and your enemies closer.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.60,1:34:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪为了让他相信我站在他这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}To make him believe I was still on his side,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.48,1:34:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我告诉他我仍然爱他 ‪我相信他说的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I told him I still love him, that I believed everything he said.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.20,1:34:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪我甚至还叫这些女孩儿贱货\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I even called these girls bitches.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.16,1:34:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我一直在给西蒙发信息说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm texting Simon all the time,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.92,1:34:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“早上好 亲爱的 你好吗 ‪晚安 好好睡吧 我爱你” ‪我想你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}saying, "Good morning, love. How are you?" "Good night. Sleep well. I love you. I miss you."
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.40,1:34:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他一直告诉我 当然 是西蒙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And he keeps on telling me, and, of course, it's Simon,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.64,1:34:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他需要钱来逃脱他敌人的追踪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}that he needed money to escape from his enemies.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.64,1:34:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他需要假护照\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He needed fake passports.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.52,1:34:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他想要我典当了车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He wanted me to pawn my car.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.80,1:34:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他想要我卖房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He wanted me to sell my house.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.24,1:34:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我必须拿到这笔钱）
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.32,1:34:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那时我就想到了 ‪我要骗这个Tinder骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}That's when I got my idea. I was going to swindle the Tinder Swindler.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.96,1:34:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙只穿名牌服装 他借此包装自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon only wears designer clothes. He's covered in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.96,1:35:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪范思哲 古驰 路易威登 杜嘉班纳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Versace, Gucci, Louis Vuitton, Dolce & Gabbana.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.48,1:35:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我在时尚奢饰品行业工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I work in the luxury fashion industry,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.84,1:35:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以我知道他的衣橱很值钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}so I know his wardrobe is worth a fortune.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.88,1:35:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我跟他说 ‪“拜托 让我替你卖了那些衣服吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I said to him, "Please, let me sell those clothes for you
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.52,1:35:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这样我们可以筹一点钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}so we can generate some money."
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.04,1:35:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（好的 你什么时候可以飞）
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.12,1:35:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙把这些衣服都带走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon has all of these clothes with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.72,1:35:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我要去布拉格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I needed to go to Prague.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.00,1:35:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪在我离开阿姆斯特丹之前 ‪西蒙给我发了一张信用卡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Before I leave Amsterdam, Simon had a credit card delivered to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.76,1:35:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪上面写着“大卫·莎伦”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It says, "David Sharon."
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.16,1:35:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我拍了张照片发给了警方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I take a picture and send it to the police,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.84,1:35:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪告诉他们西蒙又创造了一个新身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}telling them Simon is creating a new identity.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.40,1:35:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（捷克共和国 布拉格）
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.92,1:35:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他的地址在一个偏僻的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}His address was in the middle of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.12,1:36:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪随着我越来越近 我的心脏狂跳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}As I'm getting closer, my heart is pounding.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.40,1:36:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我心想 “天啊 我怎么能想出 ‪这么愚蠢的计划”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I thought, "Oh, my God, how can I come up with such a stupid plan?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.80,1:36:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“因为现在我还要面对他”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Because now I need to face him."
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.84,1:36:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他不是我男朋友 ‪他不是列维·列维耶夫的儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He's not my boyfriend. He's not the son of Lev Leviev.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.96,1:36:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他不为LLD钻石公司工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He's not working for LLD Diamonds.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.00,1:36:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他是个骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He is a fraud,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.56,1:36:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我完全不知道他会做出什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and I have absolutely no idea what he's capable of.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.76,1:36:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他已经站在外面等我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He was already standing outside waiting for me,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.36,1:36:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他抱了抱我 亲了下我的嘴唇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and he hugged me and he kissed me on the lips,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.60,1:36:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我感觉很恶心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and I felt disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.92,1:36:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我当时气得想要大喊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was so angry and I wanted to scream,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.48,1:36:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但我只对他说 “我爱你 我好想你”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}but the only thing I said was, "I love you and I missed you."
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.80,1:36:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他在布拉格市中心有预约\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He made an appointment in the center of Prague,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.84,1:36:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他希望我跟他一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and he wanted me to come along with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.60,1:36:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们在整形医院的总部外停了下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We stopped outside this head office of a plastic surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.24,1:37:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我在想 ‪“天啊 我们要在这里做什么”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was like, "Oh, my God, what are we going to do here?"
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.08,1:37:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他想改变他的颊骨 鼻子 嘴唇 ‪也许还有下巴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He wanted to change his cheekbones, his nose, his lips, maybe his chin,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.48,1:37:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪整形医生说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and the plastic surgeon says,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.56,1:37:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“很抱歉 但我不会执行这个手术\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"I'm sorry, but I'm not going to do this surgery
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.52,1:37:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为只有罪犯才会想这么做”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}because only criminals want this."
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.72,1:37:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我差点把嘴里的水吐出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I almost spit out my water
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.20,1:37:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为我真的很想告诉这位医生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}because I really wanted to say to this surgeon,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.52,1:37:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“但是他就是一个罪犯”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"But he is a criminal."
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.64,1:37:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪当我看着这个可悲的男人 ‪因为不能做整形手术哭泣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}As I'm watching this pathetic man crying for not getting his plastic surgery,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.80,1:37:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我在想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I thought,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.76,1:37:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“如果你没有这么下流卑鄙 ‪也许我还会可怜你”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"If you weren't such... a piece of shit, I would feel sorry for you."
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.24,1:37:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪到了下午 我们扮演一对情侣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}In the afternoon, we played boyfriend and girlfriend,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.68,1:37:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪牵手 一起吃晚饭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}holding hands, having dinner together.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.96,1:37:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪然后我还得睡在他旁边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}But then I needed to still sleep next to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.12,1:38:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他没有采取什么动作 谢天谢地 ‪但是我在床上一动不敢动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He didn't make any move, thank God, but I was just in bed, frozen,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.44,1:38:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪整夜都盯着天花板\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}looking at the ceiling all night.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.04,1:38:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪终于到早上了 ‪我打包了三个大行李箱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Morning finally comes, I pack up three massive suitcases.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.44,1:38:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙都没过来帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon didn't even help me with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.84,1:38:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪就在我走之前 他把一封信交给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Right before I was leaving, he hands over this letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.96,1:38:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他说 “请在飞机上看” ‪我不能很快离开那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He said, "Please read it in the plane." I cannot get out of there fast enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.20,1:38:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我记得我有这封信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I remember that I had this letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.80,1:38:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I have it here.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.08,1:39:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“亲爱的艾琳 ‪你知道这是我这辈子最艰难的时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"Dear Ayleen, well, as you know, this is the most difficult time of my life,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.12,1:39:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我想要谢谢你站在我这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and I want to thank you that you are standing by my side
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.08,1:39:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你没有放弃我们的爱”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}and that you don't give up on our love."
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.44,1:39:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“你是我梦想中的女人 ‪我想和你一起创造未来”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"You are the woman of my dreams, and I want to build a future together."
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.96,1:39:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“能和你结婚 会是我的荣幸”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"To marry you will be an honor for me."
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.24,1:39:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“生几个小孩 组建家庭 ‪你就是我脑海中的女人”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"And to make a family with kids together, you are the woman I see it with."
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.28,1:39:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“你一定要尽你所能帮助我”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"You've got to help me with everything you can."
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.84,1:39:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“这是为了你 你父母 ‪也为了我们的未来 我值得你的帮助”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"It's for you, for your parents, for our future. I'm worth it."
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.28,1:39:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“现在我该去实现不可能的奇迹了”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"Now it's time to do the impossible possible."
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.12,1:39:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“我很幸运这辈子 ‪能遇到你这样的女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"I'm blessed to have a woman like you in my life
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.28,1:39:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪并与你共度幸福的余生”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}to live in happy ever after."
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.32,1:39:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“我爱你 我从来都没这样爱过”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"I love you like I never loved before."
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.84,1:39:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“我相信你”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"I trust you."
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.52,1:39:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“不要放弃”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"Don't give up."
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.88,1:39:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“永远爱你 你的西蒙”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"Love you forever, yours, Simon."
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.36,1:39:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪真是谎话连篇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Just a piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.84,1:40:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我开始进行清仓大甩卖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm on Operation Sell, Sell, Sell.
