Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.76,1:40:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪西蒙一直在给我发短信 打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Simon is texting and calling me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.60,1:40:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（物品清单）
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.24,1:40:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪“你卖了什么 我的钱呢 你得快点”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}"What have you sold? Where's my money? You need to be quick."
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.08,1:40:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我一直跟他说我什么都没卖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I keep on telling him I haven't sold anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.40,1:40:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（已售出）
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.80,1:40:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（范思哲长裤）
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.36,1:40:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（未接语音来电）
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.60,1:40:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我一直在卖东西 ‪我就没打算把钱给他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was selling, selling, selling. I was never going to send him the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.96,1:40:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我刚收到一条通知 ‪有个人想买西蒙的一样东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I just got a notification that I got an offer for one of Simon's items.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.36,1:40:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪说曹操曹操就到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Speaking of the Devil.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.28,1:41:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪所以你现在还在卖他的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}So you're still selling his things now?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.92,1:41:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪是的 我还在卖他的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Yes, I'm still selling his things.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.12,1:41:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这当然不能填补我给他的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Of course it wasn't in line with everything that I gave him,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.40,1:41:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但感觉算是有点补偿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}but it felt like a little bit of payback.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.28,1:41:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我们周一就需要用钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}We need the money on Monday.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.00,1:41:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你总说明天 明天 ‪你是在拖延时间吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Another day, another day. Are you trying to buy time?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.28,1:41:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你把这事拖了三个星期 ‪根本用不着三个星期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}You're dragging it over three fucking weeks. It doesn't take three weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.72,1:41:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪又过了几周 ‪他就知道我把钱留给自己了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}After a few weeks, he knows that I was keeping the money for myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.76,1:41:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那时候他的态度彻底变了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}That's when he turned around completely.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.72,1:41:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你别再跟我玩了 行了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}You stop playing game with me now! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.04,1:41:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他用这些消息轰炸我 都很有攻击性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He bombs me with all these messages, and they were so aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.32,1:41:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（语音信息）
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.32,1:41:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪如果你还活着 就听我说 ‪你今天就得把钱给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}If you're active, listen to me! You're gonna give it today.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.76,1:41:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你不知道自己在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}You don't know where the fuck you're going.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.84,1:42:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪大概20分钟的语音留言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Voice memos of, like, 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.48,1:42:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我对我说的话很抱歉 ‪但事实就是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm sorry about what I said, but that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.56,1:42:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪说别人都在笑我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}But you're taking the piss out of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.96,1:42:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这就是我看清他真实面目的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}This is where I saw his several personalities.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.40,1:42:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我爱你 我关心你 我问了上千遍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I love you and I care about you. I ask a thousand fucking times.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.84,1:42:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我好声好气地请求 ‪我跟你说话很客气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I ask nicely. I'm speaking to you nicely.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.12,1:42:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我试着尊重你 但你好像在耍我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I try to respect you, but it's like you're fucking with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.84,1:42:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（语音信息）
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.84,1:42:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你不知道我有多爱你 ‪你只需要再相信我最后一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}You have no idea how much I love you. You just need to trust me one last time.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.36,1:42:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我明天需要一个答案 相信我 ‪做一次信仰之跃 去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I need an answer tomorrow. Believe in me. Have a leap of faith for one time. Do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.84,1:42:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪别骗我 我知道怎么说谎 ‪我可以教你怎么说谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Don't send me lies. I know how to lie. I can teach you how to lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.72,1:42:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我需要这笔钱才能成功\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I need this money to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.04,1:42:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（语音信息）
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.80,1:42:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（你是支持我还是反对我）
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.52,1:42:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪帮我离开这里 ‪我没有其他人了 我只有你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Help me out here. I don't have nobody else. I have only you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.92,1:42:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我求你了 拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm begging from you, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.44,1:42:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（你会失去一切）
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.00,1:42:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（语音信息）
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.00,1:42:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我给了你建议 听我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I give you advice. Choose it!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.32,1:42:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你消失了 没人能看到你的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}You disappear. Nobody can see your messages.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.40,1:42:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我不是你的敌人 我不是在跟你吵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm not your enemy. I'm not fighting you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.52,1:43:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你会遇到你这辈子见过最可怕的敌人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}And you will get the worst fucking enemy you have ever seen in your life
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.32,1:43:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪为你和你的家人考虑一下 ‪要是你敢耍我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}for you and for your fucking family if you will ever play with me!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.56,1:43:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪今天就给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Give it today.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.12,1:43:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（你像个贱人）
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.28,1:43:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪听着 艾琳 我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Look, Ayleen, I'm sorry about everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.48,1:43:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我给你最后一次警告 ‪今天 你想开战吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I give you the last fucking warning! Today. You want war?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.48,1:43:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那就开战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}You will get fucking war! You will get fucking war!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.20,1:43:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（就像我对每个人说的那样 ‪万事皆有报应）
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.08,1:43:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那是一次可怕的经历\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It was a horrible experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.12,1:43:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪但我有一点喜欢看到他“坐立不宁”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}But part of me was actually enjoying seeing him "swerm."
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.56,1:43:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪坐立不安 说错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Squirm. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.88,1:43:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（乐透抽奖）
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.04,1:43:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪艾琳 我能请你帮个忙吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Ayleen, can I ask you a favor?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.68,1:43:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你能给我买一张 ‪上面有可选号码的彩票吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Can you put me one lottery ticket with numbers that I can choose?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.16,1:43:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪你有多可悲 我还以为你是亿万富翁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}How pathetic can you be? I thought you were a billionaire.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.92,1:43:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（明天我就无家可归了）
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.44,1:43:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（你明白）
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.36,1:44:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（明天）
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.08,1:44:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他没有任何收入 他没有人可以求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He has no money coming in. He had no one to go to.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.16,1:44:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（请帮帮我 拜托 艾琳）
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.16,1:44:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（请你父母做点什么）
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.96,1:44:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他还给我发图片和消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He even sent me pictures and texts
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.00,1:44:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他在购物中心吃剩菜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}that he was eating leftovers in a shopping mall.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.40,1:44:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他长出了 像这样的大胡子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He grew himself, like, this big beard.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.16,1:44:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他睡在12美元一晚的旅馆里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He was sleeping in hostels of $12 a night.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.72,1:44:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（开心旅馆）
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.76,1:44:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（是的 旅馆）
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.40,1:44:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（一星级旅馆）
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.16,1:44:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这一刻 我看到了真正的西蒙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}At this moment, I see the real Simon,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.84,1:44:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为没有别人的钱 ‪他什么也不是 什么也做不成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}because without other people's money, he was nobody, and he's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.00,1:44:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我一贫如洗了）
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.28,1:44:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（别再演了 你就是个戏精女王）
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.40,1:44:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我没有）
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.16,1:44:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我是流浪国王）
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.44,1:44:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他还自称 “流浪国王”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He even called himself "the homeless king."
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.40,1:44:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（流浪国王）
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.48,1:45:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪钻石王子沦落到流浪国王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}The prince of diamonds to this homeless king.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.28,1:45:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪真是悲伤逆流成河\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Cry me a river.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.48,1:45:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪有一天早上 我收到他的消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}One morning, I get a text from him.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.68,1:45:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我需要机票）
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.28,1:45:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（做什么）
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.76,1:45:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（来收拾残局）
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.96,1:45:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪几周前 他提到他想去希腊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}A few weeks before, he was just mentioning he wanted to go to Greece.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.36,1:45:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（你有什么计划）
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.60,1:45:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我给他发了消息回复 他并没有读\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}When I text him back, my message wasn't receiving.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.92,1:45:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我只看到已发送\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I just saw one tick.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.28,1:45:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那时我意识到 他已经在飞机上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}That's when I realized that he was on a flight,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.80,1:45:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪因为西蒙总是手机不离手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}because Simon is always on his phone.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.84,1:45:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（今晚从布拉格飞往雅典的航班）
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.84,1:45:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我搜索从布拉格飞往雅典的航班\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I'm searching for flights from Prague to Athens.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.24,1:46:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我找到了完全符合他掉线时间的航班\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I found a flight exactly the same time as he went offline.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.64,1:46:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我把细节截屏 然后直接发给了警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I took a screenshot of the details, and I sent it directly to the police.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.80,1:46:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（紧急 ‪西蒙·列维耶夫在飞机上）
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.80,1:46:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他不会用西蒙·列维耶夫的名字 ‪坐飞机 毕竟他因为诈骗被通缉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He wouldn't travel under Simon Leviev because he was wanted for fraud.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.92,1:46:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（在用大卫·莎伦的化名）
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.88,1:46:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我也确保他们知道了我在信用卡上 ‪看到的名字 大卫·莎伦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I also make sure they had the name that I saw on the credit card, David Sharon.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.44,1:46:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（大卫·莎伦）
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.44,1:46:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（发送）
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.12,1:46:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（发送中））
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.24,1:46:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪现在就全都交给警察了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Now, it was in the hands of the police.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.72,1:46:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（在线）
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.60,1:46:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪（打字中）
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.52,1:46:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我被逮捕了）
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.52,1:46:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（我的天啊）
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.40,1:47:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪那是我人生中最美好的时刻之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}It was one of the best moments of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.44,1:47:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他甚至说）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He even says...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.32,1:47:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}‪（请帮帮我）
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.48,1:47:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他因使用大卫·莎伦名字的假护照\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}He got arrested by Interpol on a fake passport,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.88,1:47:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪被国际刑警逮捕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}under the name David Sharon.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.80,1:47:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.76,1:47:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪艾琳告诉我 抓到他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Ayleen tells me, "We got him!"
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.16,1:47:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我就想打给塞西莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I just wanted to call Cecilie.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.32,1:47:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我说 “你在开玩笑吗 ‪他真的被抓了 现在 今天”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I was like, "Are you fucking kidding me? He's really caught? Now? Today?"
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.76,1:47:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我甚至无法形容听到这个消息的喜悦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I can't even describe the joy it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.04,1:47:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪这就是我想要的 我想看他戴上手铐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}This is what I wanted. I wanted to see him in handcuffs.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.44,1:47:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪我需要替自己伸张正义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}I needed justice for myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.72,1:47:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‪他知道你把这个信息 ‪提供给警察了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs11}Does he know you gave that information to the police?
